nonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stories%20That%20Unveil%20the%20Many%20Worlds%20in%20Kerala%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144446%2Fgaurav-kumar-33Z4FsBTiAY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20availability%20of%20the%20literatures%20of%20many%20distinct%20regions%20is%20one%20of%20the%20achievement%20of%20contemporary%20Indian%20publishing.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20%3Cem%3EFeeling%20Kerala%3A%20An%20Anthology%20of%20Contemporary%20Malayalam%20Stories%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20translated%20by%20J.%20Devika%20(Penguin%2C%202023)%20is%20a%20notable%20contribution.%20The%20stories%20cover%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20themes%20as%20may%20be%20expected%20from%20a%20mature%20literary%20ethos%20%E2%80%93%20migration%2C%20ecology%2C%20social%20friction%2C%20marital%20and%20familial%20discord%2C%20political%20and%20spiritual%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20And%20few%20translators%20in%20the%20present%20have%20accomplished%20as%20much%20as%20Devika%20in%20the%20sheer%20quality%20and%20quantum%20of%20translations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevika%E2%80%99s%20introduction%20to%20the%20overall%20volume%2C%20and%20smaller%20introductions%20to%20each%20story%2C%20though%20occasionally%20polemical%2C%20gives%20us%20a%20helpful%20initial%20handle.%20The%20anthology%20succeeds%20also%20as%20the%20short%20story%20is%20a%20particularly%20favoured%20genre%20in%20India.%20The%20short%20story%20is%20not%20a%20miniature%20novel%2C%20but%20rather%20often%20captures%20the%20entirety%20of%20a%20sentiment%2C%20one%20complete%20in%20itself%2C%20and%20one%20that%20invites%20the%20reader%20to%20a%20stilled%20and%20concentrated%20contemplation.%20Many%20of%20these%20stories%20are%20worth%20re-reading%2C%20and%20often%20require%20that%20second%20reading%20to%20fully%20unpack.%20One%20cannot%20hope%20to%20summarise%20all%20the%2013%20stories%2C%20but%20a%20description%20of%20a%20few%20will%20give%20a%20flavour%20of%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20book%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20272px)%2085vw%2C%20272px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144241%2FB038273S.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22272%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144241%2FB038273S.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144241%2FB038273S-200x300.jpeg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698772%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFeeling%20Kerala%3A%20An%20Anthology%20of%20Contemporary%20Malayalam%20Stories%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ETranslated%20by%20J.%20Devika%3Cbr%3EPenguin%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYama%E2%80%99s%20story%20captures%20the%20bleak%20frustration%20and%20rage%20of%20a%20young%20woman%3A%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20had%20stored%20away%20pieces%20of%20lead%20from%20pencil%20stubs%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20ending%20her%20life%E2%80%A6%20as%20a%20child%2C%20she%20thought%20that%20all%20buses%20ran%20on%20towards%20the%20ever-receding%20horizon%E2%80%9D.%20She%20is%20trapped%20by%20a%20complaining%20mother%20and%20a%20school%20dropout%20brother%20ever%20hovering%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20criminality.%20Events%20unfold%20in%20a%20blur%20%E2%80%93%20her%20brother%2C%20perhaps%20inadvertently%2C%20kills%20the%20mother%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20steal%20her%20last%20piece%20of%20jewellery.%20The%20blur%20continues%20with%20the%20police%20arriving%2C%20the%20brother%20fleeing%2C%20and%20the%20protagonist%20needing%20to%20seek%20urgent%20employment%20to%20stave%20off%20hunger%20and%20isolation.%20Over%20the%20following%20weeks%20she%20keep%20hallucinating%20both%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20face%2C%20and%20her%20dead%20mother%20returning%20to%20demand%20her%20stolen%20gold.%20There%20are%20recurring%20surreal%20images%20of%20thefts%20at%20night%20%E2%80%93%20gold%20under%20a%20distant%20palm%20tree%20under%20a%20dark%20sky%E2%80%99s%20moon%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20not%20always%20clear%20what%20is%20real%20and%20what%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20of%20that%20female%20frustration%20and%20anger%20is%20also%20present%20in%20the%20last%20story%20by%20Shahina.%20A%20single%20street%20and%20lane%20(Street%20No.%2010%2C%20Mangala%20Lane)%20is%20used%20to%20connect%20diverse%20stories%20of%20harassment%20%E2%80%93%20within%20the%20home%20and%20bathroom%2C%20toward%20boys%20or%20girls%20scarce%20a%20decade%20old%2C%20in%20crowded%20public%20transport.%20The%20story%20ends%20with%20a%20fantasia%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseemingly%20never-ending%20line%20of%20naked%20women%E2%80%A6not%20shrinking%20in%20shame%2C%20not%20crouching%E2%80%A6%20%5Bmoving%5D%20slowly%2C%20unhurriedly%2C%20leisurely.%20Like%20the%20wind%2C%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20leaves%20and%20flowers%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20wistful%20stories%20of%20melancholy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20large%20houses%20that%20dot%20the%20Kerala%20countryside%20often%20have%20a%20single%20older%20person%20in%20them%2C%20with%20all%20their%20family%20scattered%20in%20distant%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Kerala%20anticipates%20presciently%20so%20many%20of%20the%20problems%20India%20will%20inherit%20soon%20enough%20%E2%80%93%20the%20desolation%20of%20an%20isolated%2C%20indefinite%20old%20age.%20Home%20nurses%20are%20often%20the%20last%20true%20relationships%20of%20many%20of%20these%20seniors%2C%20for%20the%20children%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20large%20photos%20on%20walls%20of%20inner%20rooms%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20end%20of%20the%20journey%20from%20illness%20to%20hospital%2C%20then%20from%20hospital%20to%20the%20restrictions%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20bed.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20hard%20sometimes%20to%20love%20that%20nurse%20even%20if%20one%20is%20grateful%20to%20her%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20smile%20of%20friendship%20lay%20dead%20on%20her%20lips%E2%80%A6when%20she%20held%20the%20thin%2C%20twig-like%20arms%2C%20Sujatha%20%5Bthe%20nurse%5D%20felt%20that%20the%20muscles%2C%20loose%20and%20hanging%2C%20were%20as%20soft%20as%20clouds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Zeherkhurani'%3A%20Nirmala%20Bhuradia's%20Latest%20Novel%20Holds%20a%20Mirror%20to%20Our%20Times%20Consumed%20by%20Hate%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fzeherkhurani-nirmala-bhuradias-latest-novel-holds-mirror-to-our-times-consumed-by-hate%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Zeherkhurani%E2%80%99%3A%20Nirmala%20Bhuradia%E2%80%99s%20Latest%20Novel%20Holds%20a%20Mirror%20to%20Our%20Times%20Consumed%20by%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20dispossessions%20too%20%E2%80%93%20Indugopan%E2%80%99s%20story%20writes%20of%20those%20who%20work%20in%20airports%20performing%20menial%20labour.%20Airports%20are%20places%20of%20middle-class%20stress%2C%20a%20stress%20often%20loaded%20onto%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20thus%2C%20when%20the%20protagonist%20Muniyandi%20is%20interrogated%20by%20a%20policeman%2C%20he%20replies%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20scared%20of%20dying%20in%20custody%2C%20Saare%20%5BSir%5D.%20The%20daily%20wages%20I%20get%2C%20my%20family%20can%20make%20if%20they%20take%20to%20begging.%E2%80%9D%20These%20men%20take%20pains%20to%20educate%20themselves%2C%20but%20this%20is%20two-edged%3A%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20your%20literacy%20will%20show%20when%20you%20speak%E2%80%94and%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20headache.%20The%20listener%20won%E2%80%99t%20like%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20a%20dispossession%20is%20only%20topped%20by%20the%20even%20more%20brutal%20maiming%20of%20harmless%20animals%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20the%20turtles%20that%20routinely%20lose%20their%20feet%20due%20to%20the%20propellers%20of%20commercial%20fishing%20that%20trouble%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20stores%20are%20examples%20of%20fine%20storytelling.%20Unni%20writes%20humorously%20of%20how%20a%20family%20in%20financial%20distress%20realises%20that%20they%20can%20refurbish%20their%20small%20house%20temple%20into%20one%20that%20claims%20to%20particularly%20cure%20sexual%20ailments%20%E2%80%93%20a%20foul-mouthed%20neighbour%20is%20promoted%20to%20oracle%2C%20a%20Bastar%20statuette%20to%20main%20deity%2C%20and%20the%20priest%20is%20given%20motivational%20books%20to%20read%20in%20case%20he%20is%20bored.%20Even%20more%20moving%20and%20elaborated%20storytelling%20(with%20themes%20of%20police%20firing%2C%20and%20the%20caste%20systems%20within%20Kerala%20Christianity)%20are%20provided%20in%20the%20exceptional%20stories%20of%20Shajikumar%20and%20Prince%20Aymanam.%20It%20would%20be%20hard%20to%20adequately%20invoke%20here%20their%20dexterity%20with%20the%20invocations%20of%20brute%20fact%2C%20heroic%20histories%2C%20corrupt%20political%20and%20media%20manipulations%20of%20caste-tragedy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20continual%20oscillations%20of%20personal%20and%20community%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevika%20retains%20the%20flavour%20of%20Malayalam%20through%20many%20means%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20through%20spelling%20(%E2%80%98intellectchuals%E2%80%9D)%2C%20by%20pronunciation%20and%20idiomatic%20usage%20(%E2%80%9C%20Now%20its%20all%20terrorists%20and%20cheats%E2%80%94comblete!%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9C%20drivers%20are%20beg%E2%80%99nning%20to%20spout%20lit%E2%80%99rature%3F%E2%80%9D)%2C%20and%20often%20by%20leaving%20the%20Malayalam%20in%20roman%20script%20before%20providing%20an%20approximate%20translation.%20The%20adept%20translations%20capture%20well%20the%20colloquial%20and%20idiomatic%20speech.%20All%20this%20helps%20restore%20verve%20and%20sparkle%20to%20a%20language%20that%20is%20always%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20dulled%20by%20translation.%20By%20keeping%20the%20pungency%20and%20heat%20of%20language%20so%20alive%2C%20Devika%20gives%20us%20as%20complete%20and%20satisfying%20a%20synoptic%20picture%20of%20the%20literary%20scene%20of%20a%20major%20culture%20as%20is%20reasonably%20possible%20in%20a%20single%20volume%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENikhil%20Govind%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20Literature%20at%20the%20Manipal%20Centre%20of%20Humanities%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708852549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25144446%2Fgaurav-kumar-33Z4FsBTiAY-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fstories-that-unveil-the-many-worlds-in-kerala%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Feeling%20Kerala%3A%20An%20Anthology%20of%20Contemporary%20Malayalam%20Stories'%2C%20translated%20by%20J.%20Devika%2C%20gives%20us%20as%20complete%20and%20satisfying%20a%20synoptic%20picture%20of%20the%20literary%20scene%20of%20a%20major%20culture%20as%20is%20reasonably%20possible%20in%20a%20single%20volume%20collection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fstories-that-unveil-the-many-worlds-in-kerala%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20speaks%20about%20mental%20strength%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708852514000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107984168%2Cimgsize-15586.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-opens-up-about-mental-strength-happiness-and-self-preservation%2Farticleshow%2F107984197.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107984197.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20strength%20and%20happiness%2C%20stating%20they%20are%20cruci