%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107983840%2Cimgsize-88178.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-enjoys-scuba-diving-off-arabia-sea-offers-underwater-prayers-in-dwarka%2Farticleshow%2F107983853.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Offering%20prayers%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8Bat%20the%20ancient%20site%20of%20Dwarka%2C%20which%20is%20immersed%20in%20waters%2C%20PM%20Modi%20called%20it%20a%20'very%20divine%20experience'.%20%26quot%3BTo%20pray%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Dwarka%2C%20which%20is%20immersed%20in%20the%20waters%2C%20was%20a%20very%20divine%20experience.%20I%20felt%20connected%20to%20an%20ancient%20era%20of%20spiritual%20grandeur%20and%20timeless%20devotion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20after%20the%20scuba%20driving%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-enjoys-scuba-diving-off-arabia-sea-offers-underwater-prayers-in-dwarka%2Farticleshow%2F107983853.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20SIMI%20Terrorist%20Was%20Arrested%20By%20Delhi%20Police%20After%2022-Year%20Manhunt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20arrested%20Hanif%20Shaikh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20proscribed%20organisation%20SIMI%2C%20after%2022%20years%20of%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20were%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20Shaikh%20since%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20him%20under%20the%20strict%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20he%20was%20charged%20with%20sedition%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaikh%20was%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20group's%20'Islamic%20Movement'%20magazine's%20Urdu%20edition%20and%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20radicalise%20several%20young%20Muslims%20through%20his%20teachings%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20WAS%20HANIF%20SHAIKH%20CAUGHT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20did%20not%20have%20much%20to%20start%20with%2C%20they%20only%20had%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BHanif%20Hudai%26quot%3B%20published%20in%20the%20magazine%20%26quot%3BIslamic%20Movement%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20only%20clue.%20This%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20identify%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaikh%20was%20living%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Bhusawal%20and%20according%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20of%20the%20Special%20Cell%2C%20Ankit%20Singh%2C%20he%20is%20a%20dreaded%20SIMI%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20cases%20against%20him%20under%20the%20UAPA%20and%20for%20anti-national%20activities%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20attending%20and%20organising%20SIMI's%20meetings%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Kerala%20and%20was%20declared%20a%20fugitive%20by%20a%20Delhi%20court%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20team%20looking%20for%20him%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years%20received%20information%20that%20Shaikh%20changed%20his%20identity%20and%20was%20now%20going%20as%20Mohammad%20Hanif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20working%20as%20a%20teacher%20at%20an%20Urdu%20medium%20municipal%20school%20in%20Bhusawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20this%20information%2C%20the%20police%20laid%20a%20trap%20on%20February%2022%20and%20caught%20him%20from%20Bhusawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20IS%20HANIF%20SHAIKH%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHanif%20Shaikh%20earned%20his%20diploma%20from%20Marul%20Jalgaon%20in%201997.%20He%20joined%20SIMI%20the%20same%20year%20and%20became%20an%20%26quot%3BAnsar%20(full-time%20worker)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20highly%20radicalized%20after%20coming%20in%20contact%20with%20SIMI%20workers.%20He%20began%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20group's%20weekly%20programmes%20and%20started%20radicalising%20young%20Muslims%20to%20join%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20by%20his%20enthusiasm%2C%20the%20then%20SIMI%20chief%20Sahid%20Badar%20made%20Shaikh%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20Urdu%20edition%20of%20'Islamic%20Movement'%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20magazine's%20editor%2C%20Shaikh%20wrote%20several%20inflammatory%20articles%2C%20wrongly%2C%20highlighting%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20he%20was%20allotted%20a%20room%20at%20the%20SIMI%20Headquarters%20in%20Delhi's%20Zakir%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20close%20relationships%20with%20Safdar%20Hussain%20Nagori%2C%20Abdus%20Shubhan%20Qureshi%20alias%20Tauqeer%2C%20Noman%20Badar%2C%20Shahnaz%20Hussain%2C%20Saif%20Nachain%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20-%20all%20members%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20police%20raid%20in%202001%2C%20Hanif%20Shaikh%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20few%20others%20and%20went%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20kept%20changing%20his%20location%20to%20evade%20arrest%20and%20finally%20made%20his%20way%20to%20Bhusawal%20from%20Jalgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20admitted%20to%20visiting%20many%20places%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20to%20motivate%20people%20to%20join%20SIMI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ban%20on%20SIMI%2C%20most%20of%20the%20active%20members%20became%20scattered.%20Some%20have%20independently%20continued%20their%20terrorist%20activities%20and%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20several%20blasts%20and%20other%20anti-national%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20time%2C%20senior%20members%20of%20%26quot%3BWahdat-e-Islam%26quot%3B%20started%20new%20organisations.%20Most%20of%20the%20members%20of%20this%20organisation%20are%20from%20SIMI.%20The%20basic%20agenda%20is%20to%20unite%20young%20Muslims%20and%20propagate%20the%20doctrine%20of%20radical%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20is%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Wahdat-e-Islam%20think%20tank%20and%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20other%20neighbouring%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20involved%20in%20collecting%20money%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20donations%20to%20support%20and%20fund%20the%20agenda%20of%20SIMI%20and%20Wahdat-e-Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20five%20siblings%20-%20three%20brothers%20and%20two%20sisters%2C%20a%20wife%2C%20and%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708851600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F82qgd47o_hanif-shaikh-simi_625x300_25_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-a-simi-terrorist-was-arrested-by-delhi-police-after-22-year-manhunt-5124072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20arrested%20Hanif%20Shaikh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20proscribed%20organisation%20SIMI%2C%20after%2022%20years%20of%20searches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-a-simi-terrorist-was-arrested-by-delhi-police-after-22-year-manhunt-5124072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-a-simi-terrorist-was-arrested-by-delhi-police-after-22-year-manhunt-5124072%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-a-simi-terrorist-was-arrested-by-delhi-police-after-22-year-manhunt-5124072%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Time%20In%20Indian%20History%3A%20R%20Ashwin%20Surpasses%20Anil%20Kumble%20For%20Major%20Feat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStar%20India%20off-spinner%20Ravichandra%20Ashwin%20on%20Sunday%20scripted%20a%20huge%20record%20during%20the%204th%20Test%20against%20England%20in%20Ranchi.%20On%20Day%203%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20Ashwin%20struck%20thrice%20in%20the%20second%20session%20as%20India%20reduced%20England%20to%20120%2F5%20at%20Tea.%20During%20his%20three-wicket%20burst%2C%20Ashwin%20became%20India's%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20home%20Tests.%20Ashwin%20surpassed%20former%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anil%20Kumble%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F265-anil-kumble-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kumble%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20elite%20list%2C%20scalping%20his%20350th%2C%20351st%20and%20352nd%20wickets.%20Kumble%2C%20who%20represented%20India%20from%201993%20to%202008%2C%20picked%20350%20wickets%20in%20Tests%20on%20home%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20is%20now%20the%20only%20player%20to%20pick%20more%20than%20350%20Test%20wicket%20in%20India.%20He%20got%20the%20wicket%20of%20Ollie%20Pope%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20wickets%20for%20India%20in%20home%20Tests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20352*%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnil%20Kumble%20-%20350%3Cbr%3E%5CnHarbhajan%20Singh%20-%20265%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20219%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20206*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%204th%20Test%2C%20Ashwin%20had%20also%20claimed%20his%20100th%20Test%20wicket%20against%20England.%20He%20became%20the%20first%20player%20to%20complete%20a%20century%20of%20wickets%20for%20India%20against%20the%20Three%20Lions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Ashwin%20reached%20the%20500%20Test%20wickets%20milestone%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20Rajkot%20Test%20and%20even%20attended%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day's%20play%20but%20had%20to%20fly%20back%20home%20because%20of%20an%20emergency.%20He%20returned%20from%20home%20on%20Sunday%20and%20bagged%20his%20501st%20Test%20wicket%2C%20prompting%20an%20emotional%20note%20from%20his%20wife%20Prithi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20yet%20fully%20known%20what%20the%20emergency%20was%20for%20Ashwin%20and%20his%20family%20but%20his%20wife%20Prithi%20summed%20up%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20saying%20those%20were%20the%20longest%2048%20hours%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20chased%20the%20500%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20To%20Vizag%2C%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20So%20I%20just%20bought%20a%20ton%20of%20sweets%20and%20gave%20it%20to%20everyone%20at%20home%20at%20499.%20500%20came%20and%20went%20quietly.%20Till%20it%20didn't.%20A%20lot%20happened%20between%20500%20and%20501.%20Longest%2048%20hours%20of%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin's%20wife%20Prithi%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20is%20about%20the%20500.%20And%20the%20499%20before%20that.%20What%20a%20phenomenal%20achievement.%20What%20a%20phenomenal%20guy.%20I%20am%20insanely%20proud%20of%20you%20Ravi%20Ashwin.%20We%20love%20you!%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708851480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0qcqgll_ravichandran-ashwin-afp_625x300_25_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2F1st-time-in-indian-history-ravichandran-ashwin-surpasses-anil-kumble-for-major-feat-5124069%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20struck%20thrice%20in%20the%20second%20session%20as%20India%20reduced%20England%20to%20120%2F5%20at%20Tea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fake%20message%20being%20shared%20on%20WhatsApp%3A%20EC%20on%20election%20date%22