t%20we%20take%20our%20problems%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20house%3F%20Similarly%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20be%20able%20to%20go%20to%20the%20highest%20authorities%20in%20the%20land%20if%20we%20have%20a%20problem%3F%20But%20what%20happens%20when%20we%20do%3F%20We%20end%20up%20getting%20beaten%2C%20teargassed%2C%20and%20shot%2C%20and%20then%20we%20end%20up%20being%20called%20the%20enemy!%20More%20and%20more%20we%20are%20being%20made%20to%20feel%20like%20outsiders%20in%20our%20own%20country.%20To%20tell%20you%20the%20truth%2C%20our%20hearts%20are%20crying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FRrz7hq3Wry8%3Fsi%3DmYwYMUupH-jP_aq9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20elderly%20farmer%20who%20had%20been%20overhearing%20the%20conversation%20interrupted.%20%E2%80%9CLook%20at%20all%20these%20farmers%20here!%20None%20of%20them%20are%20rich.%20Some%20own%20two%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20some%20three.%20Many%20of%20them%20barely%20manage%20to%20grow%20enough%20to%20feed%20even%20their%20own%20families!%20And%20yet%2C%20these%20are%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20bombed%20and%20shot!%20Modi%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20himself!%20Instead%20of%20interviewing%20us%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20interview%20Modi%20and%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20is%20doing%3F!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anger%20in%20his%20voice%20rising%2C%20the%20elderly%20man%20pointed%20to%20the%20other%20elderly%20farmers%20sitting%20there.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20knees%20are%20damaged%2C%20this%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20legs%20hurt%2C%20this%20other%20farmer%20here%20can%20barely%20walk!%20None%20of%20us%20are%20sitting%20here%20because%20we%20are%20happy%20to%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20crossed%20hundreds%20of%20tractors%20and%20trolleys%20as%20I%20walked%20towards%20the%20bridge%20across%20Ghaggar%20river%20which%20has%20now%20become%20the%20de%20facto%20border%20between%20the%20paramilitary%20and%20the%20farmers.%20Every%2050%20feet%20or%20so%2C%20someone%20had%20set%20up%20a%20%3Cem%3Elangar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20was%20serving%20tea%2C%20food%20or%20water.%20An%20elderly%20gentleman%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20tempo%20offered%20water%20bottles%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekinoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20everyone%20who%20passed%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131507%2Ffarmer-2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131507%2Ffarmer-2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131507%2Ffarmer-2-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131507%2Ffarmer-2-1024x577.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698758%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFarmers%20at%20Shambhu%20border.%20Photo%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20100%20meters%20from%20the%20paramilitary%20barricade%2C%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20stood%20guard%20next%20to%20a%20thick%20rope%20that%20had%20cordoned%20off%20a%20hundred-meter%20stretch%20of%20empty%20road%20now%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cno%20man%E2%80%99s%20land%E2%80%9D.%20The%20farmers%20have%20been%20instructed%20not%20to%20go%20beyond%20that%20rope.%20Strewn%20all%20over%20the%20road%20were%20gunny%20sacks%20which%20the%20farmers%20had%20thrown%20on%20exploding%20tear%20gas%20canisters%20to%20try%20and%20contain%20the%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20300%20metres%20from%20the%20border%2C%20a%20group%20called%20the%20United%20Sikhs%20had%20set%20up%20a%20medical%20camp%20for%20those%20injured%20in%20the%20recent%20tear%20gas%20shelling.%20They%20showed%20me%20huge%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20exploded%20tear%20gas%20cannisters%20and%20told%20me%20that%20military%20grade%20weapons%20were%20used%20on%20the%20farmers.%20They%20also%20told%20me%20that%20a%20tear%20gas%20cannister%20fired%20from%20a%20drone%20exploded%20right%20next%20to%20their%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CElderly%20people%20have%20inhaled%20tear%20gas%2C%20and%20it%20has%20damaged%20their%20lungs.%20We%20have%20removed%20pellets%20from%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20injured.%20Please%20go%20to%20Rajpura%20hospital%20and%20see%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20injured%20for%20yourself.%20What%20has%20happened%20here%20is%20very%2C%20very%20wrong!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20short%20distance%20away%2C%20Dr%20Harpreet%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Singh%2C%20two%20young%20doctors%20from%20Hoshiarpur%20were%20distributing%20medicines%20from%20the%20boot%20of%20their%20car.%20Mentioning%20their%20proximity%20to%20%E2%80%98ground%20zero%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20asked%20if%20they%20were%20afraid%20of%20getting%20injured%20in%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Harpreet%20smiled%2C%20shook%20his%20head%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20came%20here%2C%20%3Cem%3Esar%20pe%20kafan%20bandh%20ke%20aye%20thhe.%3C%2Fem%3E%20We%20came%20with%20the%20full%20awareness%20that%20we%20too%20could%20get%20injured%20or%20killed.%20But%20we%20are%20not%20afraid.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20Our%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20Ji%20Maharaj%20has%20taught%20us%20that%20just%20as%20it%20is%20a%20sin%20to%20commit%20wrongdoing%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20sin%20to%20tolerate%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20shook%20their%20hands%20and%20told%20them%20I%20admired%20their%20courage%20and%20selflessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManinder%20Singh%2C%20a%20homemaker%2C%20told%20me%20she%20comes%20every%20morning%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Eseva%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20serve%20%3Cem%3Elangar%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20protestors%2C%20and%20then%20goes%20back%20home%20in%20the%20evening.%20She%20also%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20Guru%20Nanak%20Dev%20ji%20has%20not%20made%20us%20cowards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhvir%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Sri%20Muktsar%20Sahib%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGive%20us%20MSP%20for%20all%2023%20crops%20and%20we%20will%20diversify%20our%20crop%20cultivation%20and%20grow%20the%20crops%20that%20will%20neither%20deplete%20the%20water%20table%20nor%20compel%20us%20to%20burn%20%3Cem%3Eparali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stubble)%20and%20pollute%20the%20air.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20fighting%20for%20ourselves%2C%20we%20are%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20all%20over%20India.%20Farmers%20in%20Bihar%20are%20selling%20their%20rice%20for%20Rs%201%2C300%20a%20quintal%20whereas%20MSP%20for%20rice%20is%20Rs%202%2C200.%20We%20care%20about%20them%20too.%20Give%20us%20MSP%20based%20on%20Dr%20%5BM.S.%5D%20Swaminathan%E2%80%99s%20C2%2B50%25%20formula%20and%20we%20will%20go%20home.%20We%20aren%E2%80%99t%20mad%20to%20want%20to%20sit%20here%20on%20the%20road%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25131532%2Ffarmer-3-1