20order%20of%20the%20world%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20disrupted%20by%20dangerous%20gaggles%20of%20unwashed%20juveniles%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Gaza%20directing%20rocky%20projectiles%20against%20their%20occupying%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20Can%E2%80%99t%20have%20that%2C%20what%3F%20Ask%20Fierce%20Morgan!%20I%20need%20hardly%20tell%20you%20of%20what%20the%20harvest%20has%20been%20for%20us%2C%20and%20for%20the%20civilised%20Western%20world%20at%20large.%20Suffice%20to%20say%20that%20England%20is%20in%20peril.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20think%20our%20monkey-faced%20citizens%20shared%20your%20concerns%2C%20Sir%20Marmaduke%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Richard%20Hannay%20in%20a%20quiet%2C%20level%20voice.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20if%20Rochdale%2C%20and%20that%20anarchist%20Galloway%2C%20are%20any%20sign%20of%20what%20we%20are%20up%20against.%20A%20foul%20plot%20against%20the%20Old%20Country.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20all%20up%20with%20what%20once%20made%20us%20great%20when%20they%20chucked%20apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20been%20back%20to%20the%20Cape.%20Not%20all%20the%20memories%20of%20my%20pals%20in%20Jo%E2%80%99burg%20nor%20the%20spoor%20of%20the%20wildebeest%20in%20the%20veldts%20of%20Madikwe%20will%20take%20me%20back%20there.%20But%20if%20there%20is%20a%20fighting%20chance%20of%20saving%20apartheid%20somewhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20count%20me%20in.%20I%E2%80%99m%20your%20man%E2%80%94even%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20manage%20just%20around%20thirty-nine%20steps%20at%20a%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStout%20Fella!%E2%80%9D%20murmured%20John%20Geste%2C%20once%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Legion%2C%20brother%20of%20the%20late%20Michael%20(%E2%80%98Beau%E2%80%99)%20and%20Digby%20Geste%2C%20and%20steadfast%20friend%2C%20from%20the%20days%20of%20their%20desert%20adventures%2C%20of%20the%20Cousins%20Hank%20and%20Buddy%20from%20across%20the%20Atlantic.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20count%20me%20in%2C%20too.%20Though%20it%20does%20seem%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20know%2C%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20changed%20sides%20somewhat.%20Not%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20much%20of%20a%20choice%2C%20not%20after%20that%20spot%20of%20bother%20in%20%E2%80%9939-%E2%80%9945.%20Why%2C%20even%20the%20Huns%20have%20flipped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSho%E2%80%99%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20opined%20Hank.%20%E2%80%9COne%20gen-o-cide%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20earlier%20one.%20And%20that%20ain%E2%80%99t%20all.%20It%E2%80%99s%20Uncle%20Sam%20in%20charge%20now%2C%20and%20y%E2%80%99all%20are%20its%20poodles%2C%20just%20like%20Uncle%20Sam%20is%20AIPAC%E2%80%99s%20poodle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeggin%E2%80%99%20to%20differ%2C%20Hank%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Buddy.%20%E2%80%9CMe%2C%20I%20should%20have%20said%20chihuahuas%2C%20myself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20it%20yer%20way%2C%20Buddy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hank%20amiably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20always%20the%20first%20to%20sign%20up%2C%20but%20why%20us%2C%20if%20I%20may%20ask%E2%80%94considering%20we%E2%80%99re%20around%20a%20hundred-and-forty%20years%20old%20(each%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20not%20together)%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Squadron%20Leader%20James%20Bigglesworth%20(VC%2C%20MC%2C%20DSO%2C%20DFC)%2C%20blue%20of%20eyes%20and%20square%20of%20jaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20what%20Hannay%20has%20been%20lamenting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sir%20Marmaduke%20grimly.%20%E2%80%9CThings%20aren%E2%80%99t%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20I%20find%20myself%20having%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20the%20old%20times%2C%20the%20old%20heroes%2C%20the%20old%20values.%20Our%20Armed%20Forces%20aren%E2%80%99t%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20Just%20the%20other%20day%2C%20%3Cem%3EHMS%20Useless%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EHMS%20Futility%3C%2Fem%3E%20collided%20into%20each%20other%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Bahrain.%20Eight%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20Trident%20missile%20fired%20from%20a%20Royal%20Navy%20submarine%20flew%20off%20course%2C%20and%20after%20years%20of%20working%20on%20correcting%20the%20defect%2C%20last%20month%20another%20missile%20splashed%20into%20the%20water%20close%20to%20the%20submarine.%20(It%20needs%20to%20be%20said%20though%20that%20thanks%20to%20the%20ingenuity%20of%20our%20boys%2C%20it%20missed%20the%20submarine.)%20Just%20recently%2C%20a%20malfunction%20prevented%20%3Cem%3EHMS%20Prince%20of%20Wails%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20departing%20for%20a%20NATO%20exercise%20(called%20Steadfast%20Defender%202024)%E2%80%94a%20bit%20galling%2C%20considering%20that%20%3Cem%3EPrince%20of%20Wails%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20replacement%20for%20an%20earlier%20carrier%20which%20had%20had%20to%20be%20cancelled%20because%20of%20a%20defective%20starboard%20propeller%20shaft%20coupling.%20Calling%20you%20fellows%20back%20is%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20the%20highest%20echelons%20of%20Whitehall.%20Any%20questions%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20sure%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20John%20Geste%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20I%20speak%20for%20all%20of%20us%20when%20I%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%E2%80%94er%E2%80%94an%20honour%20and%E2%80%94er%E2%80%94a%20privilege%20and%20all%20that%20for%20us%20to%20be%20called%20to%20steer%20the%20vessel%20in%20this%E2%80%94er%E2%80%94hour%20of%20need%2C%20assuming%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20unfortunate%20metaphor%20to%20employ%20in%20the%20present%20circumstances.%20As%20for%20questions%3A%20I%20can%20think%20of%20at%20least%20one%20other%20sport%20who%20would%20have%20been%20the%20first%20to%20volunteer%20on%20an%20occasion%20such%20as%20this.%20%E2%80%98Bulldog%E2%80%99%20Drummond.%20Why%20is%20he%20not%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sir%20Marmaduke%20tersely.%20Placing%20his%20finger%20on%20the%20side%20of%20his%20nose%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20take%20it%20on%20a%20need-to-know%20basis.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20suggest%20that%20I%20spell%20out%20the%20contours%20of%20your%20present%20assignment.%20Fittingly%2C%20it%20will%20be%20called%20Operation%20Resounding%20Fail%E2%80%94er%E2%80%94Victory.%20Richard%20Hannay%2C%20you%20are%20in%20charge.%20You%20will%20follow%2C%20through%20our%20remote%20tracking%20sensors%2C%20the%20infiltration%20of%20Geste%2C%20Hank%20and%20Buddy%20into%20the%20Hamas%20Chief%E2%80%99s%20secret%20headquarters%20which%20the%20CIA%20and%20MI6%20have%20now%20located%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%20The%20three%20of%20them%20will%20be%20disguised%20as%20camels.%20Bigglesworth%2C%20you%20will%20fly%20up%20from%20our%20base%20camp%20on%20the%20Israeli%20border%20with%20Gaza%20in%20your%20Camel%20Sopwith.%20The%20Finance%20fellers%20tell%20me%20the%20economy%20has%20been%20tanking%20a%20bit%2C%20so%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20quite%20been%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20advancements%20in%20aerial%20technology.%20Your%20job%20is%20to%20distract%20the%20Hamas%20Chief%20and%20his%20bodyguards%20with%20a%20series%20of%20aerobatics.%20When%20they%20step%20out%20to%20watch%20the%20fun%2C%20Hannay%20will%20have%20spotted%20them%20through%20his%20tracking%20sensors%2C%20and%20when%20he%20is%20assured%20that%20they%20have%20exposed%20themselves%20sufficiently%20to%20Geste%20and%20friends%2C%20he%20will%20whistle%20his%20favourite%20tune%E2%80%94%E2%80%98Cherry%20Ripe%E2%80%99%E2%80%94which%2C%20through%20remote%20satellite%20technology%2C%20will%20be%20conveyed%20as%20a%20signal%20to%20the%20disguised%20camels%20for%20them%20to%20reach%20for%20their%20guns%20and%20snipe%20at%20their%20target.%20That%20will%20bring%20the%20conflict%20to%20an%20end.%20I%20take%20it%20there%20are%20no%20questions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99Strewth!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Biggles%2C%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20sad%20story%2C%20and%20therefore%20best%20told%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20sentimental%20reasons%2C%20John%20Geste%20and%20Hank%20and%20Buddy%20insisted%20on%20taking%20the%20land%20route%20from%20Sidi%20Bel%20Abb%C3%A8s%2C%20via%20Fort%20Zinderneuf%2C%20to%20Gaza.%20They%20wasted%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20but%20presumably%20that%20was%20how%20they%20wanted%20it%2C%20before%20they%20staggered%20to%20their%20destination.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Biggles%20took%20his%20Sopwith%20Camel%20up%20to%20its%20designated%20spot%2C%20and%20performed%20a%20series%20of%20Himmelmann%2C%20Zimmermann%2C%20Schwitzermann%2C%20and%20Rhinemann%20turns.%20He%20also%20threw%20in%20a%20Heinemann%20turn%20for%20good%20measure.%20However%2C%20this%20did%20not%20have%20the%20desired%20effect%3A%20no-one%2C%20leave%20alone%20the%20Hamas%20Chief%20nor%20any%20of%20his%20lieutenants%2C%20made%20an%20appearance%20to%20watch%20Biggles%E2%80%99%20spectacular%20aerial%20feats.%20This%20departure%20from%20the%20script%20was%20very%20disorientating%20for%20Hannay%E2%80%94so%20disorientating%20that%20he%20began%20whistling%20a%20tune%20at%20random.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20picked%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98The%20Colonel%20Bogey%20March%E2%80%99.%20When%20you%20expect%20to%20hear%20%E2%80%98Cherry%20Ripe%E2%80%99%20but%20get%20%E2%80%98The%20Colonel%20Bogey%20March%E2%80%99%20instead%2C%20it%20can%20be%20severely%20distressing%20and%20confusing%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20are%20dressed%20up%20as%20a%20camel.%20So%20distressing%20and%20confusing%20indeed%20that%20the%20three%20camels%20unwound%20themselves%20and%20started%20firing%20wildly%20at%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohn%20Geste%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20were%3A%20%E2%80%9CStout%20Fellas!%E2%80%A6Been%20a%20lark%20to%20have%20known%20you.%20Er%E2%80%94see%20you%20in%20Valhalla.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHank%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20were%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20the%20whitest%20man%20I%20ever%20knowed%2C%20John%E2%80%94a%20reel%20Bo%20Jest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuddy%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20were%3A%20%E2%80%9CSho%E2%80%99%20thing!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20then%2C%20Biggles%E2%80%99%20Camel%20ran%20out%20of%20gas.%20After%20the%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20which%20rebounded%20on%20them%2C%20the%20West%20had%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20with%20its%20use%20of%20petrol.%20It%20is%20distressing%20to%20have%20to%20record%20that%20the%20ground%20crew%20had%20stinted%20on%20the%20fuel%20in%20Biggles%E2%80%99%20tank.%20His%20Camel%20came%20spiralling%20down%20in%20a%20crash%2C%20as%20he%20went%20West%2C%20leaving%20him%20with%20no%20time%20to%20do%20much%20more%20than%20clench%20his%20square%20jaw%2C%20narrow%20his%20blue%20eyes%2C%20and%20mutter%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99Strewth!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20his%20Whitehall%20office%2C%20Sir%20Marmaduke%20Brayton-Neigh%20straightened%20himself%20in%20his%20chair%2C%20squared%20his%20shoulders%2C%20and%20stuck%20his%20jaw%20out.%20One%20does%20not%20suppress%20the%20bulldog%20breed.%20He%20was%20not%20about%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20damned%20if%20I%20do!%E2%80%9D%20he%20muttered%20to%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20run%20out%20of%20resources.%20Not%20yet.%20Not%20while%20we%20still%20have%20the%20Famous%20Five!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20for%20the%20telephone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWoof!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Timmy%20the%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENotes%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EClubland%20Heroes%3A%20A%20Nostalgic%20Study%20of%20the%20Recurrent%20Characters%20in%20the%20Romantic%20Fiction%20of%20Dornford%20Yates%2C%20John%20Buchan%20and%20%E2%80%9CSapper%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3E%20is%20the%20title%20of%20a%20book%20by%20Richard%20Usborne.%20%3C%2Fem%3EVintage%20Stuff%3Cem%3E%20is%20the%20title%20of%20a%20novel%20by%20Tom%20Sharpe.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20name%3D%5C%22_ftn1%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Frule-br