hind%20by%20students%20from%20all%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20enrolled%20at%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Kota%2C%20who%20chose%20death%20by%20suicide.%20Look%20at%20what%20is%20common%20in%20these%20letters%E2%80%94they%20all%20say%20%E2%80%98Sorry'.%20Not%20only%20did%20these%20students%20end%20their%20lives%2C%20but%20they%20also%20blamed%20themselves%20as%20they%20took%20that%20fatal%20step.%20Sadly%2C%20we%20know%20that%20is%20not%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fleft-right-centre%2Fspate-of-suicides-in-kota-23-such-deaths-in-city-this-year-720699%5C%22%3E%2029%20student%20suicides%20were%20reported%20in%20Kota%20in%202023%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6qp4ORrLflE%5C%22%3Ehighest%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6qp4ORrLflE%5C%22%3Esince%202015.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThat's%20more%20than%20two%20suicides%20a%20month.%20Imagine%20how%20this%20news%2C%20recurring%20every%2014%20days%2C%20plays%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20students%20studying%20there.%20Each%20of%20them%20fully%20relates%20to%20such%20cases%2C%20because%20the%20stress%20that%20triggers%20every%20suicide%20is%20felt%20by%20them%20all.%20Each%20death%20must%20surely%20shake%20up%20every%20student%2C%20scarring%20them%20and%20scaring%20them%20about%20their%20own%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20we%20throw%20them%20into%20that%20cauldron%20of%20stress%20called%20Kota%20without%20a%20parachute%2C%20and%20with%20little%20guidance%20about%20what%20stress%20is%2C%20how%20it%20can%20hit%20them%2C%20hurt%20them%2C%20and%20even%20claim%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECash-Rich%20Coaching%20Centers%2C%20Yet%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20morning%20newspapers%20routinely%20carry%20full-page%20ads%20posted%20by%20all%20kinds%20of%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20right%20through%20the%20year.%20They%20flaunt%20the%20mugshots%20of%20their%20top-ranking%20students%2C%20their%20star%20lecturers%2C%20and%20often%20the%20%E2%80%98inspirational'%20founder%20of%20the%20centre.%20Along%20with%20real%20estate%20developers%2C%20paan%20masala%20companies%20and%20the%20government%2C%20these%20coaching%20institutes%20are%20among%20the%20biggest%20advertisers%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20do%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20-%20the%20size%20of%20Kota's%20coaching%20industry%20is%20pegged%20upwards%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20-%20%E2%80%8Bthey%20seem%20to%20spend%20much%20of%20it%20on%20blowing%20their%20own%20trumpets%2C%20and%20nearly%20not%20enough%20on%20creating%20a%20security%20net%20for%20their%20students.%20Perhaps%20they%20feel%20it's%20not%20their%20problem.%20Perhaps%20they%20feel%20they%20are%20there%20only%20to%20teach%2C%20and%20that%20the%20stress%20of%20preparing%20for%20competitive%20exams%20is%20for%20students%20and%20their%20families%20to%20handle.%20Not%20true.%20If%20schools%20and%20colleges%20are%20duty-bound%20to%20look%20out%20for%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20their%20students%2C%20then%20why%20not%20coaching%20centres%3F%20Especially%20when%20most%20students%20in%20Kota's%20coaching%20centres%20spend%20not%20months%20but%20years%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20often%20feel%20like%20putting%20out%20a%20full-page%20newspaper%20ad%20with%20the%20faces%20of%20students%20who%20chose%20death%20by%20suicide%20in%20Kota.%20It%20would%20help%20people%20understand%20that%20Kota's%20coaching%20centres%20do%20not%20produce%20just%20exam%20toppers.%20There%20is%20also%20this%20other%20grim%20list%20of%20those%20who%20went%20to%20the%20same%20coaching%20centres%20but%20ended%20their%20lives%20because%20they%20were%20not%20enabled%20to%20cope%20with%20pressure.%20For%20which%2C%20in%20large%20part%2C%20these%20coaching%20centres%20must%20accept%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMental%20Health%20Security%20Net%2C%20What's%20That%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6and%2C%20please%20will%20the%20government%2C%20will%20HRD%20do%20something%20about%20these%20coaching%20institutes%3F%20They%20suck%20and%20should%20be%20shut%20down%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Another%20student%2C%20another%20note.%20Look%20at%20the%20clarity%20she%20had%20on%20how%20the%20system%20was%20broken%2C%20but%20having%20so%20little%20hope%20that%20it%20could%20be%20fixed%2C%20she%20punished%20herself%20instead%2C%20taking%20her%20own%20life.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20must%20be%20a%20few%20sensitive%20professors%20in%20Kota%20giving%20good%20advice%20to%20students%2C%20but%20surely%20it%20can't%20be%20left%20at%20that.%20A%20mental%20health%20security%20net%2C%20with%20its%20various%20checks%20and%20balances%2C%20must%20be%20an%20%E2%80%98institutional'%20organ.%20And%20there%20should%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20coaching%20centres%20that%20do%20not%20put%20such%20measures%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20measures%20are%20we%20talking%20about%3F%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20a%20healthy%20student-to-lecturer%20ratio%2C%20about%20spacious%2C%20brightly%20lit%20classrooms%20and%20equally%20comfortable%20and%20welcoming%20campuses.%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20regular%20mental%20health%20counselling%20on-campus%2C%20which%20is%20easily%20accessible%20to%20students.%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20sensitisation%20of%20both%20faculty%20and%20students%20towards%20vocabulary%20that%20may%20trigger%20anxiety%20and%20thoughts%20of%20self-harm%2C%20and%20of%20how%20to%20look%20for%20signs%20that%20a%20peer%20or%20a%20student%20may%20be%20facing%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoaching%20centres%20must%20be%20assessed%20for%20whether%20they%20have%20these%20measures%20in%20place.%20It%20is%20a%20lucrative%20business%2C%20so%20they%20should%20be%20made%20to%20comply.%20If%20not%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20heavy%20price%20to%20pay%2C%20including%20the%20prospect%20of%20being%20shut%20down.%20Coaching%20centres%20are%20known%20to%20pay%20off%20government%20inspectors%20to%20get%20approvals%20and%20certifications.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20even%20now%20in%20Kota%2C%20dingy%2C%20stuffy%2C%20crowded%20coaching%20centres%20proliferate%2C%20with%20a%20destructive%20%E2%80%98do%20or%20die'%20ethos%20reigning%20supreme.%20We%20can%20only%20hope%20such%20centres%20and%20government%20inspectors%20stop%20cutting%20corners%20and%20feel%20responsible%20for%20the%20youngsters%20dying%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ELiving%20And%20Dying%20For%20%E2%80%98Dadaji's%20Dream'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIss%20bar%20hum%20hard%20work%20kar%20rahe%20the%2C%20but%20phir%20bhi%20result%20nahi%20aaya%E2%80%A6%20hamari%20himmat%20nahi%20hogi%20aapse%20nazre%20milane%20ki%20isliye...%20apni%20life%20khatam%20kar%20rahe%20hain%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(this%20year%20I%20worked%20hard%2C%20yet%20did%20not%20get%20a%20better%20result%E2%80%A6%20I%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20face%20you%2C%20so%20I'm%20ending%20my%20life)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESorry%20Dadaji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20the%20engineer%20kind...%20sorry%20for%20being%20weak..%20but%20I%20(have)%20no%20strength%20left..%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20excerpts%20from%20more%20suicide%20notes%20reveal%20the%20reality%20of%20parental%20and%20family%20pressure%2C%20against%20which%20many%20students%20are%20trying%20to%20fulfil%20their%20%E2%80%98dadaji's%20dream'%20(grandfather's%20dream)%20and%20not%20their%20own.%20Families%20often%20pin%20their%20hopes%20on%20a%20bright%20child%2C%20committing%20all%20their%20savings%20to%20the%20exorbitant%20coaching%20centre%20fees%20and%20rent%20in%20Kota.%20The%20youngster%20is%20expected%20to%20excel%2C%20get%20a%20good%20rank%2C%20get%20a%20degree%20from%20a%20prominent%20college%2C%20get%20a%20well-paid%20job%2C%20and%20transform%20the%20fortunes%20of%20the%20entire%20family.%20No%20one%20really%20asks%20the%20youngster%20what%20his%20or%20her%20preferences%20are.%20It's%20dadaji's%20dream%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%20Stress%3F%20That's%20normal.%20Suck%20it%20up.%20Go%20to%20Kota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0And%20that%20is%20the%20pressure%20cooker%20situation%20the%20youngster%20finds%20herself%20in.%20There's%20a%20coaching%20centre%20that%20says%20it's%20there%20to%20coach%20and%20not%20%E2%80%98mollycoddle'%20her%2C%20so%20she%20can't%20turn%20to%20them%20as%20her%20mind%20begins%20to%20darken.%20Her%20family%20just%20wants%20her%20to%20send%20smiling%20selfies%20with%20her%20books%20and%20keep%20up%20the%20pretence%20that%20she's%20enjoying%20fulfilling%20dadaji's%20dream.%20She%20can't%20turn%20to%20her%20family%20either.%20And%20her%20peers%2C%20all%20of%20them%20in%20the%20same%20rat%20race%2C%20mostly%20teens%20struggling%20with%20their%20own%20troubles%2C%20are%20rarely%20able%20to%20help%20either.%20And%20thus%20she%20gradually%20isolates%20herself%2C%20consumed%20by%20the%20rapidly%20building%20stress%20and%20anxiety.%20Until%20the%20pressure%20cooker%20explodes%20one%20day%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98Dadaji's%20dream'%20shatters.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBut%2C%20Where%20Are%20The%20Psychiatrists%20And%20Psychologists%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%2C%20you%20are%20studying%20psychology%2C%20and%20you%20know%20mental%20health%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20how%20much%20attention%20a%20country's%20government%20pays%20to%20it.%20In%20India%2C%20sadly%2C%20mental%20health%20gets%20very%20little%20attention.%20Even%20as%20a%20people%2C%20most%20of%20us%20are%20poorly%20informed%20and%20simply%20live%20in%20denial%20of%20mental%20health%20issues.%20The%20students%20in%20Kota%20face%20this%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20many%20don't%20come%20forward%20for%20treatment%20owing%20to%20the%20stigma%20attached%20to%20having%20a%20%E2%80%98mental%20problem'%2C%20the%20equally%20important%20fact%20is%20that%20India%20is%20glaringly%20short%20of%20mental%20health%20practitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20look%20beyond%20Kota%20for%20a%20bigger%20picture.%20In%202021%2C%20over%2013%2C000%20students%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20India.%20That's%20more%20than%2035%20a%20day.%20A%2070%25%20rise%20between%202011%20and%202021.%20Across%20India%2C%20just%20under%201%2C40%2C000%20suicides%20were%20recorded%20in%202019.%20A%202017%20study%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%20%3C%2Fem%3Esuggested%2014.3%25%20of%20Indians%20were%20dealing%20with%20mental%20illness.%20That%20is%20200%20million%20people%E2%80%94more%20than%20the%20entire%20populations%20of%20Canada%2C%20Germany%20and%20France%20put%20together!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20though%2C%20despite%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20challenge%2C%20has%20a%20ratio%20of%20just%200.75%20psychiatrists%20for%20every%201%20lakh%20people.%20This%20is%20sorely%20below%20our%20target%20of%20three%20psychiatrists%20for%201%20lakh%20citizens.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20ratio%20is%2013%20psychiatrists%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20people!%20Yes%2C%20we%20lag%20way%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPlease%2C%20No%20Kota%20Story%20Sequel%20Needed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20not%20really%20a%20shortage%20of%20funds.%20It's%20misplaced%20priorities.%20In%202020%2C%20mental%20health%20got%20just%200.05%25%20of%20the%20total%20healthcare%20budget%20of%20India.%20In%20developed%20countries%2C%20that%20share%20is%20usually%20about%205%25.%20Also%2C%20two-thirds%20of%20India's%20psychiatrists%20are%20in%20big%20cities%20alone.%20The%20number%20of%20psychiatrists%2C%20psychologists%20and%20psychiatric%20nurses%20in%20smaller%20cities%20and%20rural%20regions%2C%20is%20really%2C%20really%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20costs%20us%20thousands%20of%20lives%2C%20every%20year.%20How%20can%20that%20be%20okay%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%2C%20hopefully%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20pull%20some%20precious%20lives%20back%20from%20the%20brink%20of%20despair.%20The%20Kota%20Story%20does%20not%20need%20any%20more%20ghastly%20sequels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20commentator%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20Executive%20Producer%20of%20Investigations%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Projects%20at%20CNN-IBN%2C%20and%20is%20a%20two-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708846080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fp4vsf01o_suicide-depression-abuse-generic-unsplash_625x300_19_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fsorry-papa-forgive-me-suicide-notes-from-kotas-coaching-centres-and-a-plea-for-change-5123632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roughly%20two%20students%20die%20by%20suicide%20every%20month%20in%20Kota%2C%20India's%20coaching%20capital.%20Key%20among%20many%20other%20factors%20that%20contribute%20to%20this%20rot%20is%20the%20glaring%20lack%20of%20accountability%20the%20city's%20coaching%20centres%20enjoy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fsorry-papa-forgive-me-suicide-notes-from-kotas-coaching-centres-and-a-plea-for-change-5123632%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fsorry-papa-forgive-me-suicide-notes-from-kotas-coaching-centres-and-a-plea-for-change-5123632%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fsorry-papa-forgive-me-suicide-notes-from-kotas-coaching-centres-and-a-plea-for-change-5123632%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TBMAUJ%20becomes%20Shahid's%20third%20biggest%20hit%22%2C%22content%