%20that%20he%20continues%20to%20remain%20the%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20company.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbyju-raveendran-says-reports-of-expulsion-exaggerated-and-highly-inaccurate%5C%22%3EMr%20Raveendran%20wrote%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20employees%20denying%20media%20reports%20of%20him%20being%20ousted%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO%20and%20called%20the%20media%20reports%20%E2%80%9Cgreatly%20exaggerated%20and%20highly%20inaccurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbiz-byjus-letter%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20our%20company.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20you%20may%20have%20read%20in%20the%20media%2C%20I%20continue%20to%20remain%20CEO%2C%20the%20management%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20and%20the%20board%20remains%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbusiness%20as%20usual%E2%80%9D%20at%20BYJU'S%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20reemphasise%2C%20the%20rumours%20of%20my%20firing%20have%20been%20greatly%20exaggerated%20and%20highly%20inaccurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20just%20a%20day%20after%20shareholders%20(prominent%20investors)%20on%20Friday%20voted%20%E2%80%9Cunanimously%E2%80%9D%20to%20unseat%20Mr%20Raveendran%20from%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20this%20vote%2C%20Mr%20Raveendran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20you%20can't%20change%20the%20rules%20of%20a%20game%20midway%20without%20agreement%20from%20all%20players%2C%20we%20can't%20alter%20how%20our%20company%20is%20run%20without%20following%20these%20strict%20guidelines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Mr%20Raveendran%20claimed%20that%20the%20Extraordinary%20General%20Meeting%20(EGM)%20violated%20essential%20rules.%20Calling%20the%20meeting%20%E2%80%9Ca%20farce%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20it%20doesn't%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20yesterday's%20Extraordinary%20General%20Meeting%20(EGM)%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20essential%20rules%20were%20violated.%20This%20means%20that%20whatever%20was%20decided%20in%20that%20meeting%20does%20not%20count%20because%20it%20didn't%20stick%20to%20the%20established%20rules.%20It%20is%20crucial%20for%20everyone%20to%20understand%20the%20specific%20issues%20that%20make%20this%20EGM%20a%20farce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20key%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Raveendran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20claims%20made%20by%20a%20small%20group%20of%20select%20minority%20shareholders%20that%20they%20have%20unanimously%20passed%20the%20resolution%20in%20the%20EGM%20is%20completely%20wrong.%20Only%2035%20out%20of%20170%20shareholders%20(representing%20around%2045%25%20of%20shareholding)%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20resolution.%20That%20in%20itself%20shows%20the%20very%20limited%20support%20that%20this%20irrelevant%20meeting%20received.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20his%20brother%20are%20the%20only%20three%20members%20on%20the%20company%20board%20as%20of%20now.%C2%A0They%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20EGM%20called%20by%20a%20group%20of%20six%20investors%2C%20who%20collectively%20hold%2032%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20firm%20that%20operates%20Byju's.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708843560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fmh11kjs8_byju-raveendran-afp-650_625x300_01_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-i-continue-to-remain-ceo-byju-raveendran-day-after-shareholders-move-5123237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20growing%20trouble%20in%20the%20edtech%20firm%20Byju's%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%20Byju%20Raveendran%20told%20employees%20that%20he%20continues%20to%20remain%20the%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2