0With%202%20Key%20Allies%20Sealed%2C%20But%20Congress's%20Troubles%20Far%20From%20Over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20may%20have%20managed%20to%20secure%20its%20alliances%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20but%20its%20troubles%20are%20far%20from%20over.%20The%20main%20Opposition%20party%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20reach%20a%20seat-sharing%20understanding%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Maharashtra.%20The%20general%20election%20is%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away%2C%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20yet%20to%20begin%20its%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP's%20formidable%20election%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bengal%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Congress%20faces%20an%20uphill%20task%20to%20get%20Trinamool%20Congress%20back%20to%20the%20table.%20Trinamool%20chief%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20earlier%20declared%20that%20she%20would%20go%20solo%20after%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20seat-sharing%20fell%20through.%20The%20state%20Congress%20unit%2C%20helmed%20by%20veteran%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20bargained%20for%20about%2010%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20Trinamool%20offered%20just%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20outburst%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%2C%20in%20which%20he%20called%20her%20%26quot%3Bopportunist%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20rejected%20all%20her%20proposals.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20decided%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20in%20Bengal%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20any%20decision%20on%20an%20alliance%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20Ms%20Banerjee%20back%20on%20board%2C%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20saying%20that%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20sharp%20remarks%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20an%20understanding%20on%20seats%20so%20far.%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20continues%20to%20target%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20has%20claimed%20that%20there%20are%20difference%20within%20the%20party%20on%20whether%20to%20ally%20with%20Congress%20or%20not.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20in%20a%20dilemma.%20They%20are%20not%20saying%20officially%20that%20the%20process%20of%20forging%20the%20alliance%20has%20ended.%20The%20first%20dilemma%20is%20a%20section%20of%20the%20party%20believes%20that%20if%20they%20contest%20alone%2C%20without%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20then%20the%20minorities%20of%20West%20Bengal%20will%20vote%20against%20them.%20One%20section%20of%20the%20TMC%20wants%20the%20alliance%20to%20continue.%20Another%20section%20is%20in%20another%20dilemma%20that%20if%20the%20alliance%20is%20given%20more%20importance%20in%20Bengal%2C%20then%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20use%20ED%2C%20and%20CBI%20against%20them.%20Because%20of%20these%20two%20dilemmas%2C%20the%20TMC%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20the%20tussle%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20did%20not%20join%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20passing%20through%20Bengal%2C%20depriving%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20showcase%20optics%20that%20would%20have%20helped%20the%20alliance%20counter%20the%20BJP's%20political%20attacks%20over%20underlying%20conflict%20within%20the%20Opposition%20front.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20an%20understanding%20now%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20will%20face%20the%20tall%20challenge%20of%20hurriedly%20putting%20together%20a%20joint%20campaign%20plan%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20Maharashtra%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20too%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20a%20seat-sharing%20plan.%20Discussions%20between%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20comprising%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Balasaheb%20Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20faction%20of%20NCP%20are%20in%20the%20final%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20spoken%20to%20Mr%20Thackeray%20over%20a%20deadlock.%C2%A0The%20Congress%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20wants%20to%20contest%20three%20of%20Mumbai's%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20-%20Mumbai%20South%20Central%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20and%20Mumbai%20North%20West.%20Mr%20Thackeray%20reportedly%20wants%20to%20contest%2018%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20four%20in%20Mumbai%20-%20Mumbai%20South%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20East%20and%20Mumbai%20South%20Central.%20The%20two%20leaders%20spoke%20for%20an%20hour%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20the%20impasse.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20exits%20of%20three%20senior%20leaders%20--%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20and%20Baba%20Siddique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20has%20said%20there%20is%20no%20disagreement%20within%20the%20alliance%20and%20stressed%20that%20MVA%20will%20perform%20well%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20disagreements%20or%20dispute%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20seat%20sharing%20among%20the%20MVA%20allies.%20It%20is%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20which%20is%20in%20turmoil%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20coordination.%20The%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20will%20show%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20their%20place%20in%20the%20coming%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patole%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20challenge%20for%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20that%20two%20main%20parties%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%2C%20have%20split%20and%20their%20leaders%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20have%20lost%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol.%20A%20big%20task%20would%20be%20to%20spread%20awareness%20among%20voters%20about%20their%20new%20name%20and%20symbol%20to%20ensure%20that%20people%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20and%20backward%20areas%2C%20know%20which%20symbol%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20seat-sharing%20is%20finalised%2C%20the%20three%20parties%20will%20need%20to%20start%20joint%20campaigns%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP.%20With%20polls%20just%20months%20away%2C%20they%20are%20on%20a%20very%20tight%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Sorted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20political%20posturing%20and%20hard%20bagain%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20managed%20to%20finalise%20seat-sharing%20pacts%20with%20two%20major%20INDIA%20forces%20-%20SP%20and%20AAP.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20secured%2017%20out%20of%2080%20seats.%20In%20return%2C%20it%20has%20given%20one%20seat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party.%20With%20AAP%2C%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20has%20finalised%20seat-sharing%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Chandigarh%20and%20Goa.%20The%20two%20parties%20have%20agreed%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20they%20are%20arch-rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20there%20is%20no%20hostility%20between%20the%20allies%20over%20the%20Punjab%20arrangement.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20contest%20three%20out%20of%20seven%20seats.%20And%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20AAP%20will%20fight%20two%20out%20of%2026%20seats.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20will%20contest%208%20and%20one%20seat%2C%20respectively.%20The%20Chandigarh%20seat%20and%20two%20seats%20in%20Goa%20have%20gone%20to%20Congress%20under%20the%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20challenge%20in%20these%20seats%2C%20however%2C%20will%20be%20to%20balance%20grassroots%20leaders'%20sentiments%20with%20the%20larger%20goal%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP.%20For%20example%2C%20AAP%20securing%20the%20Bharuch%20seat%2C%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Congress%20veteran%2C%20late%20Ahmed%20Patel%2C%20has%20drawn%20strong%20reaction.%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mr%20Patel's%20son%20Faisal%20Ahmed%20Patel%2C%20have%20said%20that%20the%20party%20must%20have%20retained%20the%20seat%20for%20winnability%20alone%20and%20that%20Congress%20workers%20are%20upset.%20While%20the%20AAP%20has%20said%20it%20would%20soon%20sit%20with%20the%20Congress%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20strategy%20in%20this%20key%20seat%2C%20reaching%20an%20agreement%20may%20not%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708839900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fth9v7i6o_rahul-gandhi-mamata-banerjee_625x300_28_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-congress-seat-pact-with-2-key-allies-sealed-but-congresss-troubles-far-from-over-5123209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20may%20have%20managed%20to%20secure%20its%20alliances%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20but%20its%20troubles%20are%20far%20from%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-congress-seat-pact-with-2-key-allies-sealed-but-congresss-troubles-far-from-over-5123209%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-congress-seat-pact-with-2-key-allies-sealed-but-congresss-troubles-far-from-over-5123209%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-congress-seat-pact-with-2-key-allies-sealed-but-congresss-troubles-far-from-over-5123209%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20First%20Time%20in%20Taliban%20Era%2C%20Indian%20Technicians%20Return%20to%20Inspect%20%24265%20Million%20Dam%20in%20Afghanistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105713%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-20.56.52.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20Afghan%20Republic%20fell%20to%20the%20Taliban%2C%20India%20is%20checking%20in%20on%20the%20%24265%20million%20dam%20that%20it%20built%20in%20Afghanistan%20eight%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Salma%20dam%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20India-Afghanistan%20Friendship%20Dam%2C%20was%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20a%20global%20effort%20aimed%20at%20reconstructing%20Afghanistan%20and%20staving%20off%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20country%20having%20fallen%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Taliban%2C%20India%20had%20the%20choice%20of%20leaving%20it%20to%20the%20militant%20group%20or%20helping%20to%20maintain%20it.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20chosen%20the%20latter%2C%20sending%20a%20four-member%20team%20to%20the%20hydropower%20project%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20engagement%20with%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learned%20that%20a%20four-member%20team%20from%20the%20Indian%20public%20sector%20company%20Wapcos%20is%20currently%20visiting%20Salma%20Dam%2C%20their%20hydroelectric%20project%20built%20on%20the%20Harirud%20River%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20north-western%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20journeyed%20to%20Kabul%20via%20the%20weekly%20scheduled%20flight%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20proceeding%20to%20Herat%20city%20next%20day.%20They%20took%20a%20helicopter%20ride%20to%20the%20dam%20site%2C%20where%20they%20stayed%20for%20three%20days%20before%20embarking%20on%20their%20return%20trip.%20Local%20security%20officials%20and%20representatives%20from%20the%20Afghan%20Ministry%20of%20Energy%20and%20Water%20accompanied%20them%20throughout%20their%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weathered%20name%20board%20at%20the%20dam%20site%20mirrored%20the%20evolving%20political%20landscape%20in%20Afghanistan.%20Set%20against%20a%20blue%20backdrop%2C%20the%20inscription%20%E2%80%9CAfghan%20India%20Friendship%20Dam%E2%80%9D%20remained%20prominently%20displayed%2C%20while%20several%20other%20lines%20had%20gradually%20faded.%20On%20top%2C%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20Indian%20flag%20remained%20vibrant%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20symbol%20of%20entwined%20hands.%20But%20the%20tricolour%20flag%20of%20the%20Afghan%20republic%20along%20the%20same%20line%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20deliberately%20defaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20that%20the%20Taliban%20government%20has%20made%20repeated%20requests%20to%20Indian%20authorities%20for%20the%20dispatch%20of%20a%20technical%20team%20to%20address%20longstanding%20issues%20at%20Salma%20Dam.%20However%2C%20responding%20to%20these%20appeals%20has%20been%20delayed%20amid%20diplomatic%20complexities.%20This%20is%20likely%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20any%20Indian%20official%20delegation%20to%20Afghanistan%20related%20to%20infrastructure%20projects%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105925%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-20.56.52-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105925%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-20.56.52-1.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105925%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-20.56.52-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698740%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20technical%20team%20at%20Salma%20Dam.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20international%20community%2C%20India%20does%20not%20officially%20recognise%20the%20Taliban%20government%20in%20Afghanistan.%20However%2C%20since%20Indian%20diplomats%20returned%20to%20Kabul%20in%202022%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ftaliban-india-kabul-regional-conference-afghanistan%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520India%2520on%2520Monday%2Cconvened%2520in%2520the%2520Afghanistan%2520capital.%5C%22%3Egradual%20build-up%20of%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Taliban%2C%20despite%20the%20stationed%20diplomats%20being%20formally%20designated%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafghanistan-indian-embassy-technical-team%5C%22%3Etechnical%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20focusing%20on%20humanitarian%20assistance.%20The%20Taliban%20has%20also%20turned%20towards%20regional%20countries%20as%20prospects%20of%20formal%20diplomatic%20recognition%20from%20the%20UN%20are%20dim%20due%20to%20the%20educational%20restrictions%20on%20women%20and%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fthe-story-behind-herats-salma-dam%5C%22%3EThe%20Amazing%20Indian%20Story%20Behind%20Herat%E2%80%99s%20Salma%20Dam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Afghanistan%E2%80%99s%20two%20decade-long%20republic%20era%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20active%20presence%20in%20the%20country%20was%20anchored%20on%20its%20development%20assistance%20totalling%20over%20%242%20billion.%20In%20that%20sphere%2C%20Salma%20Dam%2C%20later%20renamed%20the%20India-Afghanistan%20Friendship%20Dam%2C%20has%20a%20premier%20position%20along%20with%20the%20Afghan%20parliament%20building%20and%20Zaranj%20Delaram%20highway%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20390px)%2085vw%2C%20390px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25110021%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-23.09.55.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25110021%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-23.09.55.jpeg%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25110021%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-23.09.55-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25110021%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-23.09.55-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698741%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22867%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20latest%20view%20from%20top%20of%20the%20dam%20towards%20the%20power%20house%20and%20the%20river.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20appointed%20state-run%20Wapcos%20to%20execute%20the%20project%2C%20the%20state%20firm%20contracted%20the%20construction%20to%20a%20joint%20venture%20of%20two%20private%20firms%2C%20SSJV%20and%20Angelique%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInaugurated%20jointly%20by%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20then%20Afghan%20President%20Ashraf%20Ghani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2Fprintrelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D145967%5C%22%3Ein%20June%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20major%20water%20infrastructure%20project%20in%20modern%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20last%2050%20years.%20The%20project%20was%20also%20diplomatically%20sensitive%20as%20Iran%20had%20objected%20to%20its%20construction%20over%20concerns%20that%20water%20flow%20in%20the%20river%20that%20crossed%20over%20into%20Iranian%20territory%20would%20reduce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20decade%2C%20amidst%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20precarious%20security%20conditions%20and%20logistical%20intricacies%2C%20the%20project%20endured%2C%20demanding%20a%20ballooning%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%201775.69%20crore%20(%24265%20million%20in%202016%20exchange%20rate)%20to%20reach%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinked%20to%20Herat%20city%20by%20a%20165-kilometre%20earthen%20road%2C%20traversable%20only%20under%20escort%20of%20a%20large%20convoy%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20the%20journey%20consumed%20seven%20to%20eight%20arduous%20hours.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20security%20landscape%20progressively%20deteriorated%20in%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20final%20years%2C%20all%20ground%20travel%20was%20abruptly%20barred%2C%20compelling%20Indian%20workers%20at%20the%20site%20to%20rely%20solely%20on%20helicopters%20for%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20commissioning%2C%20the%20dam%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Afghan%20engineers%20and%20technicians%20who%20had%20been%20trained%20in%20India.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20teams%20from%20Wapcos%20made%20occasional%20visits%20to%20the%20dam%20for%20inspections%20to%20address%20initial%20operational%20challenges.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20India%2C%20the%20main%20contractor%20sued%20Wapcos%20for%20non-payment%20of%20dues%20of%20over%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20in%20a%20case%20that%20has%20to%20be%20still%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Taliban%20started%20to%20relentlessly%20press%20their%20military%20blitzkrieg%20in%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khaama.com%2Ftaliban-kill-16-security-personnel-near-salma-dam%2F%5C%22%3Efighting%20became%20increasingly%20closer%20to%20the%20site%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20July%202021%2C%20Taliban%20entered%20Chisti%20Sharif%2C%20the%20nearest%20town%20to%20the%20dam%2C%20and%20damaged%20the%20complex%20of%20rooms%20that%20Wapcos%20had%20built%20for%20staff%20during%20the%20construction%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDevirupaM%2Fstatus%2F1426127389197692932%5C%22%3EOn%20August%2013%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20local%20Taliban%20commander%20entered%20the%20dam%20complex%20after%20the%20soldiers%20surrendered%20following%20the%20Friday%20prayers.%20Soon%2C%20the%20white%20and%20black%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdevirupam%2Fstatus%2F1427243280652283909%5C%22%3ETaliban%20flag%20fluttered%20over%20the%20dam%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%2C%20President%20Ghani%20and%20his%20aides%20fled%20to%20Uzbekistan%2C%20allowing%20the%20Taliban%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20Kabul%20and%20the%20entire%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexclusive-surrounded-by-taliban-india-built-salma-dams-future-is-uncertain%5C%22%3ESurrounded%20by%20Taliban%2C%20India-Built%20Salma%20Dam%E2%80%99s%20Future%20is%20Uncertain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20many%20of%20the%20Afghan%20engineers%20had%20migrated%20abroad%20in%20those%20uncertain%20days%2C%20the%20challenge%20in%20the%20new%20Taliban%20era%20was%20to%20find%20trained%20manpower%20to%20operate%20the%20hydropower%20project.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20attrition%20had%20begun%20months%20prior%20to%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20assumption%20of%20power%2C%20as%20salary%20payments%20dwindled%20owing%20to%20the%20Afghan%20government%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25105817%2Fsalma-dam-wapcos-staff-quarters-2022-photo-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2F