com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-former-richest-person-zong-qinghou-passes-away-at-79%2Famp_articleshow%2F107980341.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-former-richest-person-zong-qinghou-passes-away-at-79%2Famp_articleshow%2F107980341.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20First%20Person%20Account%20of%20Police%20Brutality%20on%20Peaceful%20Protestors%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25103940%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-11.00.12-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20call%20by%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20to%20observe%20February%2023%20as%20a%20Black%20Day%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20the%20young%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20and%20the%20call%20by%20CASR%20(Campaign%20Against%20State%20Repression)%20for%20a%20peaceful%20demonstration%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20security%20forces%20against%20farmers%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Jantar%20Mantar%20at%203%20pm%20on%20February%2023%20to%20express%20my%20solidarity%20with%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20entire%20area%20heavily%20barricaded%2C%20with%20a%20large%20presence%20of%20police%20and%20ITBP%20and%20not%20a%20single%20protestor.%20So%20I%20proceeded%20to%20the%20metro%20station%2C%20where%20I%20found%20a%20scattered%20group%20of%20about%2025%20students%20belonging%20to%20different%20student%20organisations%2C%20who%20had%20also%20come%20for%20the%20protest%2C%20along%20with%20another%20Delhi%20University%20teacher%2C%20N.%20Sachin.%20A%20few%20had%20brought%20placards%20protesting%20the%20repression%20on%20farmers%20and%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20their%20demands.%20We%20decided%20to%20hold%20up%20the%20placards%20and%20march%20down%20to%20Jantar%20Mantar%20raising%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20reached%20Jantar%20Mantar%20Road%2C%20the%20students%20sat%20down%20peacefully%20in%20front%20of%20the%20barricade%20raising%20slogans.%20No%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20the%20protestors%20to%20breach%20the%20barricade%20or%20create%20any%20obstruction.%20Sachin%20and%20I%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20police%20brutality%20often%20unleashed%20on%20protesting%20students%20(it%E2%80%99s%20routine%20in%20Delhi%20University)%2C%20so%20we%20had%20planned%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20police%20and%20negotiate%20with%20them%20to%20allow%20the%20students%20to%20stage%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20for%20few%20minutes%2C%20after%20which%20they%20would%20disperse.%20However%2C%20before%20we%20could%20do%20so%2C%20the%20police%2C%20without%20issuing%20any%20warning%2C%20started%20brutally%20assaulting%20and%20dragging%20the%20peacefully%20protesting%20students%20into%20the%20police%20van.%20Before%20the%20women%20police%20arrived%2C%20I%20saw%20male%20police%20manhandling%20girl%20students%20and%20protested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Sachin%20and%20I%20were%20at%20a%20distance%20from%20the%20group%2C%20as%20we%20were%20planning%20to%20go%20to%20the%20public%20meeting%20at%20the%20Constitution%20Club%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20genocide%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20detained.%20However%2C%20after%20getting%20some%20instructions%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20the%20policemen%20and%20women%20came%20after%20us%20and%20dragged%20us%20into%20the%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20most%20shocking%20was%20that%20another%20senior%20lady%2C%2065-year-old%20Sharda%20Dixit%2C%20retired%20principal%20of%20a%20government%20school%20and%20secretary%2C%20All%20India%20Save%20Education%20Committee%20(Delhi)%2C%20who%20had%20happened%20to%20come%20by%20and%20was%20standing%20some%20distance%20away%2C%20was%20manhandled%20and%20became%20unconscious.%20When%20I%20saw%20her%20condition%2C%20I%20pleaded%20with%20the%20police%20to%20let%20me%20take%20her%20to%20a%20hospital.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20threw%20her%20in%20that%20unconscious%20condition%20into%20the%20bus.%20Then%20they%20drove%20us%20around%20for%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20throughout%20which%20we%20kept%20pleading%20with%20them%20(ASI%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%2C%20ASI%20Subhash%20Chand%20and%20Constable%20Anita%20Singh)%20to%20let%20Dixit%20off%20along%20with%20a%20lady%20constable%20at%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20otherwise%20her%20life%20would%20be%20in%20danger.%20All%20our%20pleas%20fell%20on%20deaf%20ears.%20In%20desperation%2C%20I%20called%20100%20and%20the%20Senior%20Citizens%20Police%20at%201291.%20I%20got%20a%20call%20back%20from%20the%20Parliament%20Street%20Police%20Station%20and%20the%20Mall%20Road%20Police%20station%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20ASI%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%2C%20but%20he%20refused%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20noticed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20police%20and%20ITBP%20personnel%20did%20not%20have%20name%20badges.%20The%20air%20in%20the%20bus%20was%20pretty%20suffocating%2C%20and%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20that%2C%20to%20prevent%20students%20from%20sticking%20their%20heads%20out%20of%20windows%20of%20the%20bus%20for%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%2C%20the%20police%20used%20thick%20sticks%20though%20other%20windows%20to%20beat%20them%20back%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Dixit%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Parashar%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20ongoing%20atrocity%20and%20contacted%20some%20officers%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20finally%20stopped%20at%20a%20farm%20house%20next%20to%20Kapashera%20Police%20Station%2C%20from%20where%20the%20local%20SHO%20took%20Dixit%20and%20me%20to%20the%20nearby%20Deepayan%20Hospital.%20There%20her%20BP%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20extremely%20high%2C%20177%2F97.%20After%20some%20oral%20medication%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20government%20hospital%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Hospital%2C%20in%20Sector%209%2C%20Dwarka%2C%20for%20further%20treatment.%20Around%208%20pm%2C%20she%20and%20I%20were%20%E2%80%98handed%20over%E2%80%99%20to%20her%20daughter%20who%20came%20to%20pick%20her%20up.%20I%20boarded%20the%20metro%20and%20reached%20home%20around%209%3A30%20pm.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20Sachin%20and%20the%20students%20who%20had%20been%20detained%20were%20also%20released%20from%20Kapashera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Dixit%20had%20severe%20body%20ache%20and%20a%20splitting%20headache%20following%20the%20outrageous%20trauma%20inflicted%20on%20her%20on%20Friday.%20She%20is%20planning%20to%20undergo%20a%20thorough%20medical%20examination%20for%20internal%20injuries%20and%20any%20other%20medical%20complication%20that%20may%20have%20arisen%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENandita%20Narain%20is%C2%A0Associate%20Professor%20(Retd)%2C%20St.%20Stephens%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%3B%20Former%20President%2C%20DUTA%20and%20FEDCUTA%3B%20and%20President%2C%20Democratic%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Front%20and%20Chairperson%2C%20Joint%20Forum%20for%20Movement%20on%20Education.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708837827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25103940%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-11.00.12-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fa-first-person-account-of-police-brutality-on-peaceful-protestors-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20who%20lost%20consciousness%20was%20denied%20medical%20care%3B%20male%20police%20officials%20manhandled%20female%20students.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fa-first-person-account-of-police-brutality-on-peaceful-protestors-in-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Melania%20Trump's%202018%20%26quot%3BI%20Really%20Don't%20Care%26quot%3B%20Zara%20Jacket%20Was%20Message%20For...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20time%20former%20US%20First%20Lady%20Melania%20Trump%20stirred%20up%20a%20massive%20controversy%20when%20she%20stepped%20out%20to%20attend%20a%20children's%20charity%20in%20an%20olive%20jacket%20from%20Zara%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20care%2C%20do%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3F%20She%20wore%20the%20jacket%20in%20June%202018%20as%20she%20boarded%20an%20Air%20Force%20plane%20to%20visit%20the%20Upbring%20New%20Hope%20Children's%20Shelter%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20immigrant%20children%20separated%20from%20their%20parents%20during%20border%20crossings%20were%20put%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumour%20mills%20worked%20overtime%20to%20decode%20what%20the%20message%20meant%20and%20who%20it%20was%20for%2C%20while%20Melania's%20supporters%20and%20detractors%20waged%20a%20war%20over%20her%20fashion%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20a%20new%20book%20claims%20to%20spill%20it%20all%20about%20the%20raging%202018%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Katie%20Rogers'%20upcoming%20book%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Woman%3A%20The%20Transformation%20of%20the%20Modern%20First%20Lady%2C%20from%20Hillary%20Clinton%20to%20Jill%20Biden%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20jacket%20was%20most%20definitely%20a%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20was%2C%20however%2C%20aimed%20neither%20at%20the%20children%20nor%20the%20%26quot%3Bleft-wing%20media%26quot%3B%20as%20Melania%20had%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20controversy%2C%20Melania%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20obvious%20I%20didn't%20wear%20the%20jacket%20for%20the%20children...%20It%20was%20for%20the%20people%20and%20for%20the%20left-wing%20media%20who%20are%20criticising%20me.%20I%20want%20to%20show%20them%20I%20don't%20care.%20You%20could%20criticise%20whatever%20you%20want%20to%20say.%20But%20it%20will%20not%20stop%20me%20from%20doing%20what%20I%20feel%20is%20right.%26quot%3B%20She%20criticised%20the%20media%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bobsessed%26quot%3B%20with%20her%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jibe%20was%20at%20her%20step-daughter%20Ivanka%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20was%20locked%20in%20a%20battle%20for%20four%20years%2C%20only%20pausing%20to%20renegotiate%20her%20pre-%20and%20post-nuptial%20arrangements%20with%20her%20husband%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20new%20book%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20feud%20began%20when%20Melania%20Trump%20didn't%20move%20into%20the%20White%20House%20right%20away%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Trump's%20presidency%20to%20let%20her%20son%20Barron%2C%20then%2010%2C%20finish%20his%20school%20year%20in%20New%20York.%20As%20Ivanka%20decided%20to%20re-do%20the%20East%20Wing%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Melania%20jumped%20right%20in%20to%20resist%20it%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20four-year-long%20%26quot%3Binternal%20power%20struggle%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20aware%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20suggested%20that%20his%20eldest%20daughter%20would%20be%20helping%20to%20share%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20being%20First%20Lady%2C%20and%20this%20was%20not%20a%20development%20that%20pleased%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eldest%20daughter%20intended%20to%20take%20over%20the%20First%20Lady's%20quarters%20and%20eliminate%20her%20role%20essentially%2C%20making%20it%20%26quot%3Bgeared%20to%20serving%20the%20entire%20First%20Family%2C%20not%20just%20the%20First%20Lady%26quot%3B%2C%20Rogers%2C%20New%20York%20Times'%20White%20House%20correspondent%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20her%20father's%20backing%20as%20Trump%20pushed%20for%20Ivanka%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20alongside%20Melania.%20He%20even%20told%20reporters%20when%20he%20began%20his%20tenure%20that%20his%20daughter%20would%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20her%20(Melania)%20and%20work%20with%20her%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20First%20Lady%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Melania%20dismissed%20any%20such%20attempts%2C%20kickstarting%20her%20bitter%20battle%20with%20her%20stepdaughter%20she%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Princess%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Ivanka%20served%20as%20an%20advisor%20in%20her%20husband's%20West%20Wing%2C%20Melania%20and%20she%20mostly%20avoided%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Lady%20believed%20it%20was%20inappropriate%20for%20Ivanka%2C%20her%20brothers%2C%20and%20all%20their%20spouses%20to%20be%20so%20exhaustively%20involved%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20she%20ever%20waged%20a%20battle%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20is%20one%20she%20clearly%20lost%3A%20For%20four%20years%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20see%20where%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20family%20business%20stopped%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rogers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708837440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fmelania-trump-jacket-reuters_625x300_1529629384974.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmelania-trumps-2018-i-really-dont-care-zara-jacket-was-message-for-step-daughter-ivanka-trump-5123085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remember%20the%20time%20former%20US%20First%20Lady%20Melania%20Trump%20stirred%20up%20a%20massive%20controversy%20when%20she%20stepped%20out%20to%20attend%20a%20children's%20charity%20in%20an%20olive%20jacket%20from%20Zara%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20care%2C%20do%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmelania-trumps-2018-i-really-dont-care-zara-jacket-was-message-for-step-daughter-ivanka-trump-5123085%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmelania-trumps-2018-i-really-dont-care-zara-jacket-was-message-for-step-daughter-ivanka-trump-5123085%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.