%2C%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20citizen%20shall%20have%20the%20right%20to%20profess%2C%20practice%20and%20propagate%20his%20religion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFreedom%20of%20faith%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fundamental%20tenets%20of%20Islam.%20But%20sadly%2C%20in%20matters%20of%20religion%2C%20tempers%20flare%20up%20and%20the%20Qur%E2%80%99anic%20mandate%20is%20forsaken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708776923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fprotests-death-threats-against-pakistan-chief-justice-as-bail-granted-to-blasphemy-accused%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20reports%2C%C2%A0the%20judge%20had%20to%20face%20online%20backlash%20and%20even%20thinly%20veiled%20death%20threats%20after%20he%20ordered%20the%20release%20of%20a%20man%20from%20the%20Ahmadi%20sect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fprotests-death-threats-against-pakistan-chief-justice-as-bail-granted-to-blasphemy-accused%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20Presents%20Proposal%20for%20Post-War%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20proposed%20a%20plan%20for%20postwar%20Gaza%2C%20which%20foresees%20the%20Israeli%20military%20retaining%20security%20control%20over%20the%20coastal%20Palestinian%20enclave%20after%20the%20war%20with%20Hamas%20ends%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-netanyahu-unveils-plan-for-postwar-gaza%2Flive-68352843%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20p