posal%2C%20saying%20it%20means%20%26quot%3Breoccupying%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20and%20obstructing%20American%20and%20international%20efforts%20to%20establish%20the%20Palestinian%20State.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnetanyahu-presents-proposal-for-post-war-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Insides%20and%20Outsides'%3A%20Arbab%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20Documentary%20Is%20a%20Tender%20Tale%20of%20Bearing%20Witness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24135539%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-1.55.04-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20a%20young%20Muslim%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20to%20make%20an%20honest%20film%20about%20their%20own%20%E2%80%9CMuslim-ness.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20even%20harder%20to%20make%20one%20that%20foregrounds%20their%20own%20private%20self%20and%20family.%20It%20is%2C%20generally%2C%20also%20not%20easy%20to%20make%20a%20film%20based%20on%20introspective%20mind-chatter%20without%20boring%20the%20audience.%20Arbab%20Ahmad%2C%20through%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20manages%20to%20do%20all%20three%20with%20grace%2C%20patience%20and%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%E2%80%99s%2054-minute%20documentary%2C%20which%20was%20his%20thesis%20film%20at%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%20and%20first%20premiered%20at%20the%20International%20Documentary%20and%20Short%20Film%20Festival%20of%20Kerala%20in%20August%2C%20is%20an%20unassuming%20auto-portrait%20of%20an%20individual%20and%20his%20parents%20grappling%20with%20tectonic%20shifts%20around%20them%20in%20their%20own%20mundane%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24140124%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-2.00.48-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24140124%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-2.00.48-PM.png%20546w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24140124%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-2.00.48-PM-300x190.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22598%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EArbab%20Ahmad%2C%20director%20and%20producer%20of%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20And%20Outsides%3C%2Fem%3E%20receiving%20the%20Kumar%20Talkies%20Award%20for%20Best%20Editing%20in%20a%20long%20documentary%20from%20Kerala%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40iffklive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20title%20suggests%2C%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20about%20two%20worlds%3A%20the%20household%20and%20the%20country%3B%20the%20family%20and%20the%20society.%20Ahmad%20finds%20himself%20awkwardly%20lodged%20between%20these%20poles%2C%20discovering%20and%20rediscovering%20his%20own%20self%20%E2%80%93%20and%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20mean%20to%20be%20a%20Muslim%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%3F%20The%20film%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20a%20conclusive%20answer%2C%20perhaps%20because%20there%20is%20none.%20So%2C%20with%20sombre%20honesty%20and%20humility%2C%20it%20merely%20attempts%20to%20answer%20that%20question%20through%20personal%20ethnography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowhere%20does%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eassume%20that%20every%20Muslim%20person%20or%20family%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20would%20feel%20the%20same%20way%20about%20the%20pandemonium%20around%20them%20as%20Arbab%20and%20his%20parents%20do.%20Yet%2C%20there%20is%20a%20profound%20universality%20in%20their%20story%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20dismiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20Ahmad%20uses%20two%20voices%20when%20he%20talks%20about%20himself%20or%20his%20feelings%20%E2%80%93%20first%20and%20third%20person.%20When%20he%20uses%20the%20latter%2C%20he%20refers%20to%20himself%20by%20name%2C%20as%20if%20in%20an%20out-of-body%20experience.%20One%20may%20see%20this%20astral%20projection%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20Muslim%20self%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20that%20often%20finds%20itself%20questioning%20its%20own%20identity%2C%20choices%20and%20ideologies%20from%20a%20distance.%20This%20internal%20fracturing%20of%20the%20Muslim%20self%20is%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20most%20severe%20repercussions%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20onslaught%20that%20the%20community%20is%20being%20subjected%20to%20in%20India%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20able%20to%20effortlessly%20oscillate%20between%20the%20home%20and%20the%20world%2C%20the%20mundane%20and%20the%20extraordinary%2C%20precisely%20because%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20pretend%20to%20be%20something%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20a%20grand%20ideological%20treatise%20about%20%3Cem%3EMuslim-ness%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20India.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20able%20to%20uncompromisingly%20talk%20about%20the%20politics%20of%20majoritarian%20violence%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20nonchalance%20of%20daily%20life%20in%20a%20middle-class%20Muslim%20household%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20political%20and%20the%20personal%20melt%20into%20each%20other%20without%20one%20completely%20diluting%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20motif%20in%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%3A%20movement.%20He%20consciously%20dwells%20on%20it%20through%20the%20film%20using%20the%20dual%20pivots%20of%20space%20and%20time.%20Muslims%20in%20India%20have%20always%20been%20on%20the%20move%20since%20the%20Partition.%20They%20continue%20to%20be%20so%20even%20today%20%E2%80%93%20not%20because%20they%20want%20to%2C%20but%20because%20they%20are%20forced%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20himself%20is%20moving%20houses%2C%20as%20his%20father%20retires%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%20after%2041%20years%20in%20service%20as%20a%20professor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20arrived%2C%20bringing%20along%20even%20more%20uncertainty%2C%20worry%20and%20prejudice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20restive%2C%20nothing%20is%20the%20same%20anymore%20%E2%80%93%20from%20their%20house%20to%20the%20world%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20strongest%20motif%20in%20%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%3A%20resilience.%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20mother%20talks%20about%20sectarian%20violence%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20the%20steady%20unravelling%20of%20the%20culture%20of%20respect%20while%20cooking%20biryani%20and%20admonishing%20her%20husband%20for%20driving%20too%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20frame%2C%20his%20father%20directs%20his%20son%20to%20move%20the%20camera%20away%20from%20him%20and%20instead%2C%20film%20the%20posing%20peacock%20in%20the%20lawn%2C%20and%20in%20the%20next%20frame%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20shuffling%20through%20old%20files%20to%20ascertain%20which%20of%20his%20documents%20would%20stand%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%E2%80%99%20(NRC)%20test.%20The%20contradictions%20chill%20the%20spine%2C%20but%20their%20infectious%20smiles%2C%20visible%20in%20nearly%20every%20frame%2C%20warm%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20seamlessly%20merge%20images%20and%20sounds%20is%20conspicuous%20throughout%20the%20film.%20In%20one%20scene%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20reading%20out%20the%20case%20details%20of%20various%20Muslim%20individuals%20who%20were%20lynched%20by%20Hindu%20mobs%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20for%20allegedly%20carrying%20beef%20or%20the%20COVID-19%20pathogen.%20As%20he%20does%20that%2C%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20mother%20knocks%20at%20the%20door%20and%20calls%20him%20out%20%E2%80%93%20the%20din%20growing%20louder%20and%20more%20frantic%20by%20the%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fzeherkhurani-nirmala-bhuradias-latest-novel-holds-mirror-to-our-times-consumed-by-hate%5C%22%3EZeherkhurani%E2%80%99%3A%20Nirmala%20Bhuradia%E2%80%99s%20Latest%20Novel%20Holds%20a%20Mirror%20to%20Our%20Times%20Consumed%20by%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20juxtaposition%20of%20his%20factual%20recitation%20and%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20knocks%20ends%20up%20creating%20a%20harrowing%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20and%20claustrophobia.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20walls%20around%20Ahmad%20were%20rapidly%20closing%20in%20on%20him.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20ends%20up%20conjuring%20a%20profound%20audio-visual%20metaphor%20for%20the%20plight%20of%20an%20average%20Indian%20Muslim%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20is%20also%20sharply%20aware%20of%20his%20own%20class%20privileges%20as%20a%20Muslim%20born%20into%20a%20well-off%20family%2C%20protected%20by%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20generational%20security.%20He%20understands%20that%20Muslims%20from%20economically%20marginalised%20backgrounds%20face%20greater%20risks%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20%E2%80%93%20a%20point%20that%20becomes%20clear%20when%20he%20explains%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20as%20they%20stand%20on%20a%20foot%20over%20bridge%20atop%20the%20erstwhile%20protest%20site%20at%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20why%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20interview%20some%20of%20the%20locals%20on%20camera.%20Shaheen%20Bagh%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20yet%20another%20recurring%20motif%20in%20the%20film%2C%20both%20as%20a%20Muslim%20ghetto%20and%20a%20site%20of%20righteous%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInsides%20and%20Outsides%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20an%20ideological%20manifesto.%20It%20is%2C%20rather%2C%20a%20deeply%20personal%20diary%20of%20a%20pensive%2C%20perplexed%20and%20perturbed%20self%20that%20today%20finds%20itself%20dangling%20between%20two%20different%20worlds%3B%20a%20collection%2C%20even%2C%20of%20intimate%20thoughts%20jotted%20hurriedly%20on%20small%20pieces%20of%20paper%3B%20as%20assortment%20of%2C%20as%20Ahmad%20himself%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdrafts%20on%20moving%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20tender%20story%20of%20bearing%20witness%20to%20political%20tumult%2C%20and%20of%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20thank%20Ahmad%20for%20letting%20us%20bear%20witness%20alongside%20him%2C%20for%20generously%20opening%20the%20doors%20of%20his%20home%20for%20us%2C%20and%20for%20telling%20a%20story%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAngshuman%20Choudhury%20is%20an%20associate%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708776052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24135539%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-1.55.04-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Finsides-and-outsides-arbab-ahmads-documentary-is-a-tender-tale-of-bearing-witness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20title%20suggests%2C%20'Insides%20and%20Outsides'%20is%20about%20two%20worlds%3A%20the%20household%20and%20the%20country%3B%20the%20family%20and%20the%20society.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Finsides-and-outsides-arbab-ahmads-documentary-is-a-tender-tale-of-bearing-witness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Private%20Hospitals%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Accept%20PMJAY%20Patients%20Due%20to%20Over%20Unpaid%20Dues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F04140813%2F6872410817_7beee43941_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Csymbolic%20protest%E2%80%9D%2C%20private%20hospitals%20of%20Gujarat%20have%20decided%20to%20not%20accept%20patients%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20subsidised%20health%20insurance%20scheme%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20from%20February%2026%20to%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMJAY%20Private%20Empanelled%20Private%20Hospital%20Association%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%93%20the%20umbrella%20body%20comprising%20789%20private%20and%20charitable%20hospitals%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20pending%20amount%20of%20Rs%20300%20crore%20due%20to%20the%20hospitals%20be%20cleared%20first%20to%20sustain%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20health%20insurance%20scheme.%20However%2C%20it%20gave%20a%20call%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Csymbolic%20protest%E2%80%9D%20after%20failing%20to%20receive%20no%20written%20assurance%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2013%2C%20the%20association%20briefed%20the%20press%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20where%20it%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20not%20paid%20dues%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20and%20a%20number%20of%20private%20and%20trust-run%20hospitals%20are%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20verge%20of%20bankruptcy%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fdues-pending-hospitals-wont-accept-pmjay-patients-from-february-26-29-9176165%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20that%20Association%20also%20claimed%20that%20multiple%20representations%20to%20the%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20went%20unheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20we%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20office%20of%20Gujarat%20Health%20Minister%20Rushikesh%20Patel%20for%20a%20meeting%20on%20February%2021.%20We%20met%20Principal%20Secretary%20(Health)%20Dhananjay%20Dwivedi%20and%20other%20officials%20but%20they%20only%20orally%20assured%20us%20that%20our%20issues%20will%20be%20resolved%20and%20refused%20to%20give%20us%20anything%20in%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20association%E2%80%99s%20media%20spokesperson%20Dr%20Ramesh%20Chaudhary%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20proceed%20with%20our%20symbolic%20protest.%20The%20hospitals%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20accept%20any%20patient%20under%20PMJAY%20from%20February%2026%20to%2029.%20If%20our%20issues%20remain%20unresolved%20even%20after%20that%2C%20we%20may%20proceed%20to%20not%20accept%20patients%20under%20PMJAY%20indefinitely%20and%20intensify%20our%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20Association%20also%20complained%20about%20%E2%80%9Cunexplained%20deductions%20and%20rejection%20of%20claims%20by%20the%20insurance%20company%20Bajaj%20Allianz%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708775053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F04140813%2F6872410817_7beee43941_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgujarat-private-hospitals-wont-accept-pmjay-patients-due-to-over-unpaid-dues%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20PMJAY%20Private%20Empanelled%20Private%20Hospital%20Association%20Gujarat%20had%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20pending%20amount%20of%20Rs%20300%20crore%20due%20to%20the%20hospitals%20be%20cleared%20first%20to%20sustain%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20health%20insurance%20scheme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgujarat-private-hospitals-wont-accept-pmjay-patients-due-to-over-unpaid-dues%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%E2%80%99s%20Call%20for%20370%20Seats%20Is%20Echoed%20by%20Bollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Firked-by-fascism-charge-modis-censors%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20exhorting%20his%20party%20workers%20to%20work%20for%20370%20seats.%20He%20predicts%20the%20BJP%20itself%20will%20get%20that%20number%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20allies%2C%20get%20around%20400.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20303%20seats%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20pretty%20big%20jump%20of%20about%2067%20seats%2C%20not%20an%20easy%20electoral%20feat%20that%20Modi%20is%20predicting.%20Why%20370%3F%20If%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20touch%20a%20two-third%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20358%20seats%20should%20be%20enough.%20Nor%20is%20370%20higher%20than%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20400%20plus%20in%20the%201984%20elections.%20So%20how%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20this%20Article%20was%20the%20first%20major%20decision%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20after%202019.%20Lest%20voters%20forget%2C%20this%20call%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20remind%20them%20of%20that.%20And%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20the%20television%20channels%20will%20do%20their%20part%2C%20constantly%20talking%20about%20Mission%20370%20on%20the%20nightly%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20clever%20by-half%20tactic%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20it%20specialises%20in.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20always%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20its%20agenda%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget.%20And%20they%20corral%20social%20media%20supporters%2C%20mainstream%20Godi%20media%20and%20of%20course%20fellow%20traveller%20popular%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20on%20cue%2C%20arrives%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20film%20starring%20Yami%20Gautam%20and%20Arun%20Govil%20(who%20once%20played%20Ram%20in%20the%20TV%20serial%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20synopsis%20of%20the%20film%20on%20the%20site%20%E2%80%98Book%20my%20Show%2C%E2%80%99%20where%20one%20can%20buy%20tickets%20for%20movies%2C%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202016%20Kashmir%20unrest%2C%20a%20young%20local%20field%20agent%2C%20Zooni%20Haksar%2C%20is%20picked%20out%20by%20Rajeshwari%20Swaminathan%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20for%20a%20top-secret%20mission.%20Their%20aim%3F%20Cracking%20down%20on%20terrorism%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20billion-dollar%20conflict%20economy%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20by%20doing%20the%20absolute%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20abrogating%20the%20notorious%20Article%20370.%20That%20too%2C%20without%20spilling%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20innocent%20blood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20guns%2C%20explosions%2C%20and%20killings%20nonetheless%20follow%2C%20as%20per%20the%20trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trailer%20of%20the%20film%20also%20shows%20Gautam%20saying%2C%20earnestly%2C%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20is%20a%20lost%20case.%20Until%20the%20special%20status%20exists%2C%20we%20cannot%20even%20touch%20them.%20Nor%20will%20they%20allow%20us%20to%20change%20it.%E2%80%9D%20But%20then%20come%20our%20heroes%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20fiery%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20telling%20Parliament%20that%20it%20is%20being%20removed.%20As%20if%20we%2C%20the%20ordinary%20public%2C%20do%20not%20get%20the%20message%2C%20the%20(real)%20prime%20minister%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fit-will-help-people-get-correct-information-pm-modi-on-upcoming-movie-about-article-370-5094687%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20film.%20Tax%20exemption%20will%20no%20doubt%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20is%20this%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20Waiting%20in%20the%20wings%20is%20%3Cem%3EBastar-The%20Naxal%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20title%20should%20explain%20what%20this%20could%20be%20about%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20have%20doubts%2C%20the%20teasers%2C%20as%20trailers%20are%20called%20now%2C%20will%20clear%20them.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20give%20away%20too%20many%20spoilers%2C%20but%20it%20opens%20with%20an%20angry-looking%20woman%20(Adah%20Sharma%2C%20last%20seen%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E)%20speaking%20to%20the%20camera%20and%20informing%20us%20that%20the%20wars%20with%20Pakistan%20killed%20only%208%2C738%20Indian%20soldiers%2C%20while%20in%20this%20very%20nation%2C%20Naxals%20have%20killed%20over%2015%2C000%20Indian%20jawans.%20When%20Bastar%20Naxals%20killed%2076%20jawans%20cruelly%2C%20there%20were%20celebrations%20in%20JNU!%20Apparently%20%E2%80%98Left-liberal%20pseudo-intellectuals%E2%80%99%20are%20great%20supporters%20of%20these%20Naxals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20films%20that%20are%20also%20being%20made%2C%20a%20biopic%20of%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20and%20Kangana%20Ranaut%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EEmergency%3C%2Fem%3E.%20No%20doubt%20a%20few%20more%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20such%20overly%20nationalistic%20and%20propaganda%20films%20have%20been%20successful.%20A%20recent%20biopic%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20sank%20without%20a%20trace%2C%20as%20did%20Akshay%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20big-budget%20%3Cem%3ESamrat%20Prithviraj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20touted%20as%20a%20Hindutva%20film.%20But%20small%20films%20without%20stars%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20did%20well%20and%20such%20movies%20do%20get%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20succeed%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20flops%20or%20hits%2C%20each%20of%20these%20films%20adds%20to%20the%20noise%20it%20creates%20and%20are%20force%20multipliers.%20They%20confirm%20the%20prejudices%20of%20its%20followers%20and%20potential%20voters%2C%20especially%20from%20a%20younger%20demographic%20who%20will%20probably%20%E2%80%98learn%E2%80%99%20their%20history%20from%20this.%20And%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20open%20support%20for%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20will%20throw%20its%20full%20weight%20behind%20those%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20thinks%20will%20help%20its%20mission%20of%20getting%20those%20370%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708774247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmodis-call-for-370-seats-is-echoed-by-bollywood%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%20It's%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20J%26amp%3BK%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20this%20Article%20was%20the%20first%20major%20decision%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20after%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmodis-call-for-370-seats-is-echoed-by-bollywood%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Defeat%20to%20Trump%20looms%20over%20Nikki%20