%20the%20investment%20amounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Vinod%20used%20the%20profits%20to%20expand%20pearl%20farming%20in%20four%20ponds%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20two%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B1.25%20acre%5D.%20In%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%20each%20pearl%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20was%20thrice%20the%20investment%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Many%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20often%20visit%20Vinod's%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342926%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMany%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20often%20visit%20Vinod%E2%80%99s%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20success%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20easy.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20I%20had%20failed%20miserably%2C%20my%20family%20doubted%20my%20capabilities%20and%20I%20had%20to%20face%20negative%20comments%20as%20I%20had%20forcefully%20established%20a%20pond%20inside%20our%20home%20and%20exhausted%20a%20huge%20sum.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20setback.%20I%20focused%20on%20using%20this%20failure%20as%20my%20motivation%20and%20to%20prove%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEventually%2C%20many%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20started%20visiting%20my%20farm%20and%20I%20was%20being%20called%20at%20agritech%20fairs%20across%20the%20state.%20I%20have%20received%20recognition%20from%20former%20chief%20ministers%20and%20an%20appreciation%20letter%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20This%20has%20given%20me%20immense%20motivation%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20at%20this%20age.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20have%20managed%20to%20earn%20an%20identity%20by%20doing%20something%20unique%20sitting%20in%20my%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2045-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20informs%20that%20he%20wishes%20to%20establish%20a%20training%20institute%20for%20farmers%20interested%20in%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89574%2Fsanjay-gandate-pearl-farmer-gadchiroli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20so%20only%20when%20I%20get%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20authorisation.%20A%20farmer%20needs%20loans%20when%20starting%20something%20new.%20For%20this%2C%20they%20need%20to%20show%20certification.%20I%20lack%20that%20authority.%20Not%20everyone%20can%20go%20to%20Odisha%20to%20learn%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20request%20the%20state%20government%20to%20help%20me%20in%20this%20regard%20as%20I%20myself%20have%20seen%20unemployment%20days%20and%20I%20wish%20that%20I%20provide%20job%20opportunities%20to%20the%20unemployed%20with%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%2