3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20can%20guess%20which%20one%20thrived!%20Once%20the%20lockdown%20eased%20in%202021%2C%20Akshay%20approached%20IIT%20Kanpur%20where%20he%20met%20Dr%20Amitabha%20Bandopadhyay%20who%20helped%20him%20access%20labs%2C%20office%20space%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20a%20NIDHI%20Prayas%20Grant%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20along%20with%20financial%20support%20of%20around%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20also%20boosted%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%E2%80%99s%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Akshay%20was%20joined%20by%20Mukesh%20Singh%2C%20Shubhendra%20and%20Raj%20Kamal%20in%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20this%20fertiliser%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20why%20crops%20seem%20to%20be%20loving%20the%20LCB%20fertiliser%2C%20Akshay%20says%20it%20is%20because%20it%20provides%20them%20with%20everything%20they%20were%20missing%20in%20other%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimply%20put%2C%20the%20fertiliser%20has%20four%20components.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20microbes%20%E2%80%94%20nitrogen-fixing%2C%20potassium-mobilising%2C%20phosphorus-solubilising%2C%20and%20Trichoderma.%20This%20set%20helps%20the%20plant%20access%20the%20nutrients%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20grow%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20component%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20biomass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20comprises%20seven%20types%20of%20biomass%20such%20as%20bagasse%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20etc.%20The%20third%20component%20is%20the%20nanoparticles%20which%20increase%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20microbes%20and%20help%20them%20survive%20in%20areas%20where%20it%20is%20hot.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20thermophilic%20so%20that%20the%20microbes%20can%20survive%20at%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2070%20degrees%20celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342919%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20health%20of%20crops%20has%20visibly%20increased%20after%20farmers%20used%20the%20Navyakosh%20fertilisers%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342920%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20health%20of%20crops%20has%20visibly%20increased%20after%20farmers%20used%20the%20Navyakosh%20fertilisers%2C%20says%20Akshay%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fourth%20component%20is%20a%20polymer%20which%20holds%20260%20times%20its%20weight%20in%20water%20and%20helps%20plants%20in%20drought-prone%20regions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LCB%20fertiliser%20helps%20reduce%20the%20cost%20for%20a%20farmer%20(from%20Rs%206600%20for%20one%20acre%20to%20Rs%204000%20for%20an%20acre)%20while%20making%20the%20process%20hassle-free.%20Because%20of%20the%20polymer%2C%20farmers%20only%20have%20to%20irrigate%20the%20land%20once%20in%2025%20days%20in%20contrast%20to%20once%20in%2015%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Akshay%20claims%20that%20over%2035%2C000%20farmers%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20product.%20As%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%20are%20adopting%20this%20new%20piece%20of%20wonder%2C%20Akshay%20says%20he%20feels%20it%20is%20a%20personal%20win.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20what%20farmers%20have%20to%20endure%20because%20of%20products%20that%20do%20not%20perform%20well.%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20that%20I%20can%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708610946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-1708603905.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Shrivastav%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineer%2C%20launched%20'Navyakosh'%2C%20a%20unique%20fertiliser%20rich%20in%20microbes%20that%20can%20help%20farmers%20increase%20their%20productivity.%20He%20started%20his%20company%2C%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20in%20his%20backyard%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic-induced%20lockdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342901%2Ffarmer-income-success-lcb-fertilizers-biofertiliser-navyakosh-akshay-shrivastav-iit-kanpur-labs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Dad%E2%80%99s%20a%20Farmer%20%26amp%3B%20This%20Was%20a%20Dream%E2%80%99%3A%20Engineer%20Grows%20Rare%20%E2%80%98Yellow%20Dates%E2%80%99%2C%20Reaps%20Big%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20the%20country%20are%20heading%20towards%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20only%20a%20few%20turn%20towards%20farming.%20Affected%20by%20various%20factors%2C%20especially%20high%20risk%20and%20low%20profitability%2C%20no%20farmer%20would%20want%20his%20son%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20perspective%20towards%20taking%20up%20farming.%20But%20I%20was%20very%20sure%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20career%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the