rive%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Viji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20water%20lilies%20require%20a%20minimum%20of%20six%20hours%20of%20direct%20sunlight%20daily%2C%20which%20may%20pose%20challenges%20in%20colder%20regions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Happy%20Pot%2C%20Happy%20Plant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20pot%20depends%20on%20the%20purpose%20of%20your%20planting%20the%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20bloom%20them%20for%20personal%20purposes%2C%20then%20big%20pots%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20for%20flowers%20to%20grow%20would%20be%20perfect.%20The%20plants%20do%20not%20go%20dormant%20easily%20and%20bloom%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20are%20planting%20for%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20then%20smaller%20pots%20would%20be%20ideal%20for%20you%20as%20they%E2%80%99re%20easier%20to%20sell%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELilies%20can%20bloom%20in%20pots%20as%20small%20as%206%20inches%20and%20as%20large%20as%2018%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lilies%20need%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20to%20thrive.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-7-1708088864