surrounded%20by%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Idukki%20district%2C%20used%20to%20be%20a%20hub%20for%20millets%2C%20cultivating%20nearly%2018%20varieties%20until%20three%20decades%20ago.%20However%2C%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Chinnar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20poses%20a%20challenge%20for%20farmers%20due%20to%20animals%20like%20boars%20and%20elephants%20damaging%20their%20millet%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20consumerism%20grew%20and%20the%20sale%20of%20rice%20increased%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20millets%20declined.%20This%20too%20affected%20the%20tribal%20community%20living%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20lacking%20access%20to%20a%20proper%20market%20for%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%202023%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Year%20of%20the%20Millet%E2%80%99%2C%20Lenovo%20aimed%20to%20revive%20this%20traditional%20superfood%20in%20Kanthalloor%2C%20as%20shared%20by%20Pratima%20Harite%2C%20Head%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20CSR%20%26amp%3B%20Philanthropy%20at%20Lenovo%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20idea%20to%20mobilise%20the%20community%20using%20technology%2C%20Lenovo%20first%20surveyed%20227%20households%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Egrama%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20found%20that%20over%2060%20percent%20of%20households%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivated%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20in%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20their%20land%20i.e.%20below%2020%20cents.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20case%20earlier%2C%20according%20to%20Mohandas%2C%20who%20states%20that%20over%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20land%20was%20used%20to%20cultivate%20millets%20a%20few%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20help%20these%20farmers%20go%20back%20to%20their%20roots%20and%20start%20cultivating%20millets%20again%2C%20this%20time%20empowered%20with%20the%20help%20of%20technology%2C%20training%20and%20marketing.%20We%20believe%20that%20smart%20technology%20solutions%20have%20the%20power%20to%20transform%20communities%20and%20revive%20lost%20traditions.%20This%20technology%20would%20also%20help%20the%20younger%20generation%20take%20the%20information%20forward%20in%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pratima%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Work%20for%20Humankind%E2%80%99%20initiative%20has%20partnered%20with%20Dream%20India%20Network%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20implementation%20partner%3B%20the%20Grama%20Panchayat%20for%20eco-tourism%20and%20farmer%20engagement%3B%20IHRD%20College%20for%20Applied%20Sciences%2C%20Kanthalloor%2C%20for%20setting%20up%20their%20technology%20centre%3B%20and%20Samudra%20Network%20and%20Agri%20app%20as%20their%20digital%20integration%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20activity%20that%20Lenovo%20undertook%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Dream%20India%20Network%2C%20was%20to%20choose%2025%20farmers%20%E2%80%94%2016%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20%E2%80%94%20from%20five%20wards%20and%20convince%20them%20to%20sow%20millets%20in%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20land.%20They%20were%20given%20good-quality%20seeds%20and%20taught%20different%20ways%20to%20revive%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20farmers%20were%20already%20growing%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20self-consumption.%20We%20asked%20them%20to%20try%20growing%20any%20of%20the%20other%20five%20varieties%20in%2050%20cents%20of%20their%20unused%20land%20by%20instilling%20confidence%20that%20we%20would%20market%20it.%20Since%20the%20land%20was%20already%20used%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20earlier%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20problem.%20Furthermore%2C%20millets%20grow%20in%20low-fertility%20soils%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20too%20much