ach%20homestay%20in%20Kanthalloor.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Parackal%20says%20they%20are%20creating%20linkages%20with%20exporters%20to%20sell%20millets%20once%20the%20yield%20increases%20and%20are%20also%20working%20with%20the%20Kerala%20Government%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20department%20to%20widen%20the%20processing%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhakrishnan%2C%20a%20farmer%20who%20is%20part%20of%20the%20programme%20and%20former%20president%20of%20Devikulam%20block%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20expressed%20happiness%20at%20the%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20traditional%20food%3B%20we%20have%20started%20consuming%20unhealthy%20food%20only%20over%20the%20past%2030%20years.%20It%20came%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20good-quality%20seeds%20to%20sow.%20Lenovo%20helped%20us%20source%20good%20quality%20seeds%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20us%20get%20a%20good%20harvest.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20of%20an%20even%20better%20yield%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20harvest%20produced%20more%20than%201%2C800%20kg%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20company.%20Encouraged%20by%20this%20success%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20involve%2025%20additional%20farmers%2C%20each%20with%20an%20acre%2C%20expanding%20millet%20cultivation%20to%20cover%2075%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%20volunteers%20helped%20gather%20data%20and%20analyse%20the%20impact%20of%20solutions%2C%20helping%20farmers%20access%20the%20necessary%20apps%2C%20and%20building%20awareness%20for%20market%20linkages.%20They%20are%20also%20providing%20digital%20access%20to%20information%20on%20Government%20programmes%20and%20millet%20cultivation%20methods%20to%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mohandas%20informs%20that%20he%20is%20boosting%20the%20production%20of%20millet%20by%20giving%20subsidies%20to%20124%20farmers%20from%20next%20year.%20Kannamma%20Gopalan%2C%20on